Name: Main switch
Help:
Start / stop of refrigeration. 
With this setting refrigeration can be started, stopped or a manual override of the outputs can be allowed. (For manual control the value is set at -1. Then the outputs can be force controlled. Start / stop of refrigeration can also be accomplished with the external switch function connected to a DI input.
Stopped control will give a ”Main switch OFF" alarm.
Help_en:
Start / stop of refrigeration. 
With this setting refrigeration can be started, stopped or a manual override of the outputs can be allowed. (For manual control the value is set at -1. Then the outputs can be force controlled. Start / stop of refrigeration can also be accomplished with the external switch function connected to a DI input.
Stopped control will give a ”Main switch OFF" alarm.
Help_zh:
制冷起/停。可以通过该参数开启，停止和手动控制输出。（需要手动控制时，r12=-
1。可以强制控制输出。制冷起/停控制也可通过外部开关量信号实现(DI)。
制冷停止时，控制器将显示“Standby alarm（待机模式）”
Help_da: Start / stop af regulering. Med denne indstilling kan reguleringen startes, stoppes eller sættes i manuel overstyring. Ved manuel overstyring kan udgangene overstyres. Reguleringen kan også startes og stoppes vie et digitalt indgangssignal, hvis en sådan indgang er sat op.Når reguleringen stoppes aktiveres en alarm, for at gøre opmærksom på dette.
Help_fr:
Marche / Arrêt du régulateur
Avec ce paramètre, le régulateur peut être démarré, arrêté ou une commande manuelle des sorties peut être autorisée. (Pour le contrôle manuel, la valeur est définie sur -1).
Help_es: Paro/Marcha de la refrigeración. Con este ajuste la refrigeracion se inicia, se para o se pone el controlador en manual (ajustado en este caso un -1). Si se pone en manual, se puede actuar sobre las salidas. Tambien puede haber un interruptor externo en una entrada digital.
Help_de:
Start / stop of refrigeration. 
With this setting refrigeration can be started, stopped or a manual override of the outputs can be allowed. (For manual control the value is set at -1. Then the outputs can be force controlled. Start / stop of refrigeration can also be accomplished with the external switch function connected to a DI input.
Stopped control will give a ”Main switch OFF" alarm.
Help_pt: Função início/parada. Com essa configuração a refrigeração pode ser iniciada, parada ou ter as saídas colocadas para manual. Para controle manual o valor deve ser definido para -1, e então as saídas podem ser forçadas. Inicio/parada da refrigeração pode ser feita com a chave externa conectada à uma DI.
Help_ru:
Включение/выключение охлаждения. Этот параметр запускает регулирование, останавливает или переводит в режим ручного управления выходами. (Для режима ручного управлениянужно выбрать значение -1. 
Тогда выходами можно управлять принудительно. Запуск/остановека охлаждения также может быть осуществлена через внешний цифровой вход.
Help_it:
Start / stop of refrigeration. 
With this setting refrigeration can be started, stopped or a manual override of the outputs can be allowed. (For manual control the value is set at -1. Then the outputs can be force controlled. Start / stop of refrigeration can also be accomplished with the external switch function connected to a DI input.
Stopped control will give a ”Main switch OFF" alarm.

Name: Delay of outputs at power up
Name_en: Delay of outputs at power up
Name_fr: Tempo des sorties à la mise sous tension
Name_es: Retraso de salidas a la conexion
Name_it: Delay of outputs at power up
Help:
Delay of output signal after start-up 
After start-up or a power failure the controller’s functions can be delayed so that overloading of the electricity supply network is avoided.  
Here you can set the time delay.
Help_en:
Delay of output signal after start-up 
After start-up or a power failure the controller’s functions can be delayed so that overloading of the electricity supply network is avoided.  
Here you can set the time delay.
Help_zh:
启动后的输出信号延时。
可设置控制器在启动或电源故障后，控制输出的延时，减少对电网的冲击。此处可设置延时时间。
Help_da: Forsinkelse af udgangssignaler efter en strømafbrydelse. Funktionen anc´vendes til at forhindre en overbelastning af al-nettet after en strømafbrydelse.
Help_fr: Délai avant l'enclenchement des sortie après une mise sous tension
Help_es: Retraso de las salidas al dar tension al equipo o al haber un fallo de tensión. Aqui se ajusta el retraso de las salidas.
Help_de:
Delay of output signal after start-up 
After start-up or a power failure the controller’s functions can be delayed so that overloading of the electricity supply network is avoided.  
Here you can set the time delay.
Help_pt: Atraso dos sinais de saída após iniciar ou após falha de energia.
Help_ru: Задержка выходного сигнала после подачи питания. После запуска или проблем с питанием функции контроллера могут быть задержаны во избежание перегрузки электрической сети. Здесь можно установить временную задержку
Help_it:
Delay of output signal after start-up 
After start-up or a power failure the controller’s functions can be delayed so that overloading of the electricity supply network is avoided.  
Here you can set the time delay.

Help:
Selection of application 
The controller covers several applications for control of a refrigerated case. Here you set which of the possible applications is required.
This menu can only be set when regulation is stopped, i.e. “r12 Main Switch” is set to 0.
Help_en:
Selection of application 
The controller covers several applications for control of a refrigerated case. Here you set which of the possible applications is required.
This menu can only be set when regulation is stopped, i.e. “r12 Main Switch” is set to 0.
Help_zh: 选择应用类型。控制器包含多种制冷应用类型，可在此处选择需要的一种。该参数只有在控制停止时才能更改，如r12=0的时候。
Help_da: Valg af anvendelse. Regulatoren dækker flere anvendelsesmuligheder for styring af et kølemøbel. Hér vælger du den anvendelse, der passer til det pågældende møbel eller kølerum. Værdien kan kun ændres når hovedafbryderen er sat i OFF position.
Help_fr: Selection de l'application disponible dans le régulateur. Ce paramètre n'est réglable que lorsque le régulateur est a l'arret, ex: "r12 inter Principal" réglé à 0.
Help_es: Seleccion de la aplicación. El controlador tiene una serie de aplicaciones de refrigeracion dependiendo de este ajuste. Este parametro solo se puede cambiar si el interruptor principal esta parado.
Help_de:
Selection of application 
The controller covers several applications for control of a refrigerated case. Here you set which of the possible applications is required.
This menu can only be set when regulation is stopped, i.e. “r12 Main Switch” is set to 0.
Help_pt: Seleção da aplicação. O controlador cobre diversas aplicações para controle refrigerado. Aqui você define qual delas será usada. Este menu só pode ser alterado com funcionamento PARADO, ou seja, r12=0.
Help_ru: Выбор применения. Контроллер охватывает несколько вариантов управления охлаждаемой витриной. Здесь Вы выбираете какое  требуется применение из возможных. В этом меню можно меять настройки только когда регулирование остановлено, например "r12 Главный Выключатель" настроен на 0.
Help_it:
Selection of application 
The controller covers several applications for control of a refrigerated case. Here you set which of the possible applications is required.
This menu can only be set when regulation is stopped, i.e. “r12 Main Switch” is set to 0.

Name: Refrigerant
Help:
Select the type of refrigerant. If the required refrigerant is not part of the list, the user defined option can be used. Please contact Danfoss for detailed information

Warning: Wrong selection of refrigerant may cause damage to the system.
Help_en:
Select the type of refrigerant. If the required refrigerant is not part of the list, the user defined option can be used. Please contact Danfoss for detailed information

Warning: Wrong selection of refrigerant may cause damage to the system.
Help_zh:
选择制冷剂类型。如果想使用的制冷剂不在列表里，可以选择用户定义项，此时，请联系Danfoss了解详细信息。
注意：选取不对应的制冷剂会对系统造成损坏。
Help_da:
Vælg kølemiddel. Hvis det ønskede kølemiddel mangler kan det indstilles vha. brugerdefinerede konstanter. Kontakt venligst Danfoss for yderligere information.

Advarsel: Hvis der indstilles et forkert kølemiddel kan det medføre skader på systemet.
Help_fr: Sélectionnez le type de rérigérant. Si le réfrigérant requis n'apparait pas dans la liste, vous pouvez utiliser Refri. Perso. . Merci de contacter Danfoss pour plus de détailsATTENTION: une mauvaise sélection peut gravment endommager votre systeme.
Help_es: Seleccione el tipo de refrigerante. Si el refrigerante no esta en la lista, se puede usar la opcion de refrigerante de usuario.
Help_de:
Select the type of refrigerant. If the required refrigerant is not part of the list, the user defined option can be used. Please contact Danfoss for detailed information

Warning: Wrong selection of refrigerant may cause damage to the system.
Help_pt: Selecione o tipo de refrigerante. Se o refrigerante não estiver na lista, a opção "definido pelo usuário" pode ser utilizada. Contacte a Danfoss para informações detalhadas. Aviso: seleção errada do refrigerante pode causar danos ao sistema.

Name: Temperature sensor type
Help:
Sensor type for S3, S4 and S5. 
Normally a Pt 1000 sensor with great signal accuracy is used. But you can also use a sensor with another signal accuracy. That may either be a PTC sensor (1000 ohm at 25°C) All the mounted sensors S3-S5 must be of the same type. 

0 = Pt 1000

1 = PTC 1000

2 = NTC 5k

3 = NTC 10k
Help_en:
Sensor type for S3, S4 and S5. 
Normally a Pt 1000 sensor with great signal accuracy is used. But you can also use a sensor with another signal accuracy. That may either be a PTC sensor (1000 ohm at 25°C) All the mounted sensors S3-S5 must be of the same type. 

0 = Pt 1000

1 = PTC 1000

2 = NTC 5k

3 = NTC 10k
Help_zh: S3、S4和S5温度传感器的类型。通用使用Pt1000，精度较高，也可以选择其它类型的探头，如PTC1000。S3、S4和S5传感器的类型必须一致。0=Pt1000，1=PTC1000，2=NTC 5k，3=NTC 10k。
Help_da:
Følerytpe for S3, S4 and S5 følerne. 
Normalt anvendes en Pt1000 føler med høj nøjagtighed. Alle de anvendte S3-S5 følere skal være af samme type. 

0 = Pt 1000

1 = PTC 1000

2 = NTC 5k

3 = NTC 10k
Help_fr: Type de sonde pour S3, S4 et S5. Normalement une sonde PT1000 avec un signal précis doit etre utiisée. Mais il est possible d'utiliser un autre type de sonde. Ce peut etre une PTC (1000 ohm à 25°C). Toutes les sonde S3 à S5 doivent etre du meme type. 0 = Pt10001 = PTC 10002 = NTC 5k3 = NTC 10k
Help_es:
Tipo de sensor de temperatura. Normalmente se usa un sensor Pt1000 que tienen mucha precisión, pero se pueden usar otro tipo de sensores. La sonda S2 debe ser siempre Pt1000, pero los demas pueden ser los siguientes:
0 = Pt1000
1 = PTC1000
2 = NTC 5K
3 = NTC 10K
Help_de:
Sensor type for S3, S4 and S5. 
Normally a Pt 1000 sensor with great signal accuracy is used. But you can also use a sensor with another signal accuracy. That may either be a PTC sensor (1000 ohm at 25°C) All the mounted sensors S3-S5 must be of the same type. 

0 = Pt 1000

1 = PTC 1000

2 = NTC 5k

3 = NTC 10k
Help_pt: Tipo de sensor para S3, S4 e S5. Em geral é utilizado um PT1000, mas você pode utilizar outro sensor. Entre eles um PTC (1000 ohm à 25°C). Todos os sensores S3-S4-S5 precisam ser do mesmo tipo. 0= PT1000, 1= PTC, 2= NTC5K, 3= NTC10K.
Help_ru:
Тип датчика для S3, S4 и S5.
Обычно используется датчик Pt 1000 с высокой точностью сигнала. Но Вы также можете использовать датчик с другой точностью сигнала.  Это может быть также датчик PTC (1000 Ом при 25 град. С). Все установленные датчики S3-S5 должны быть одного типа.
Help_it:
Sensor type for S3, S4 and S5. 
Normally a Pt 1000 sensor with great signal accuracy is used. But you can also use a sensor with another signal accuracy. That may either be a PTC sensor (1000 ohm at 25°C) All the mounted sensors S3-S5 must be of the same type.

1 = PTC 1000

2 = NTC 5k

3 = NTC 10k

Name: Service pin
Help:
If the controller is built into a LonWorks network with data communication, it must have an address, and the system manager must know this address.
The address is sent to the system manager when the menu is set in pos. ON. 
IMPORTANT: Before you set o04, you MUST set the application mode of the controller (The function is not used when the data communication is MODBUS)
Help_en:
If the controller is built into a LonWorks network with data communication, it must have an address, and the system manager must know this address.
The address is sent to the system manager when the menu is set in pos. ON. 
IMPORTANT: Before you set o04, you MUST set the application mode of the controller (The function is not used when the data communication is MODBUS)
Help_zh:
当控制器通过LonWorks搭建通讯网络，需要油地址，同时系统控制器必须能识别到该地址。当该参数设为ON时，控制器将把地址发送到系统控制器。
重要：在设置服务密码前，需要设置控制器的应用模式（如果使用Modbus，该功能不被使用）
Help_da:
Hvis regulatoren er tilsluttet et LonWorks netværk, så skal man først sætte adressen og derefter kan man sende adressen til system manageren ved at sætte service pin parameteren i ON position.

Vigtigt: For nogle regulatorer skal anvendelsen indstilles først førend service pin aktiveres
Help_fr: Si le régulateur est installé sur un réseau LON, celui-ci doit avoir une adresse, et le SM doit connaitre cette adresse. L'adresse est envoyée au SMen mettant le Service Pin sur ON.
Help_es:
If the controller is built into a LonWorks network with data communication, it must have an address, and the system manager must know this address.
The address is sent to the system manager when the menu is set in pos. ON. 
IMPORTANT: Before you set o04, you MUST set the application mode of the controller (The function is not used when the data communication is MODBUS)
Help_de:
If the controller is built into a LonWorks network with data communication, it must have an address, and the system manager must know this address.
The address is sent to the system manager when the menu is set in pos. ON. 
IMPORTANT: Before you set o04, you MUST set the application mode of the controller (The function is not used when the data communication is MODBUS)
Help_pt: Se o controlador estiver em uma rede LonWorks, ele tem um endereço, e o gerenciador do sistema conhece este endereço. O endereço é enviado ao gerenciador quando o parâmetro é definido na posição ON. IMPORTANTE: antes de definir o o04 você precisa definir o modo de aplicação do controlador.
Help_ru: Если контроллер интегрирован в сеть передачи данных LonWorks, он должен иметь адрес, и блок мониторинга должен знать этот адрес. Адрес отправляется блоку мониторинга, когда параметр установлен в положение ВКЛ. Важно: Перед настройкой o04, должно быть выбрано применение.
Help_it:
If the controller is built into a LonWorks network with data communication, it must have an address, and the system manager must know this address.
The address is sent to the system manager when the menu is set in pos. ON. 
IMPORTANT: Before you set o04, you MUST set the application mode of the controller (The function is not used when the data communication is MODBUS)

Name: Thermostat mode
Help:
Here it is defined how the thermostat is to operate. Either as an ordinary ON/OFF thermostat or as a modulating thermostat.
When operation is ”modulating” the valve will limit the flow of refrigerant so that the temperature variation will be less than for the ON/OFF thermostat.
The thermostat differential (r01) must not be set lower than 2K for ""modulating"".
In a decentralised plant you must select the ON/OFF thermostat setting."
Help_en:
Here it is defined how the thermostat is to operate. Either as an ordinary ON/OFF thermostat or as a modulating thermostat.
When operation is ”modulating” the valve will limit the flow of refrigerant so that the temperature variation will be less than for the ON/OFF thermostat.
The thermostat differential (r01) must not be set lower than 2K for ""modulating"".
In a decentralised plant you must select the ON/OFF thermostat setting."
Help_zh:
此处可定义温控方式，在常用ON/OFF模式与调制模式中选取。
当选择为调制模式时，控制器会通过AKV阀限制制冷剂的流动，使温度变化会比ON/OFF时小，此时，温差（r01）设定值不能高于2K。在分散控制系统中，必须选择ON/OFF模式。
Help_da: Hér vælges det om temperatur reguleringen skal køre som en normal ON/OFF termostat eller modulerende med konstant køling. Ved modulerende termostat begrænses væskeindsprøjtningen i fordamperen således at temperaturen holdes konstant omkring udkoblingsværdien + 1/2 differens. Differensen bør aldrig stilles lavere end 2 K. For møbler med indbygget kompressor skal man vælge ON/OFF termostat.
Help_fr: Tout ou rien ou modulant
Help_es: Aqui se define como debe funcionar el modo de termostato del controlador. Puede ser un modo ON/OFF o un modo modulante. Si se elige el modo modulante el controlador limita el flujo de refrigerante para que se mantenga la temperatura mas o menos constante, en este caso el diferencial del termostato debe ser al menos 2K.
Help_de:
Here it is defined how the thermostat is to operate. Either as an ordinary ON/OFF thermostat or as a modulating thermostat.
When operation is ”modulating” the valve will limit the flow of refrigerant so that the temperature variation will be less than for the ON/OFF thermostat.
The thermostat differential (r01) must not be set lower than 2K for ""modulating"".
In a decentralised plant you must select the ON/OFF thermostat setting."
Help_pt: Aqui você define se o termostato irá operar. Mesmo que seja definido como termostato ON/OFF ou termostato modulante. Quando a operação é modulante a válvula irá limitar o fluxo de refrigerante, portant oa variação de temperatura será menor que no modo ON/OFF. o diferencial (r01) não deve ser definido para um valor menos que 2K.
Help_ru: Здесь определяется как должен работать термостат. Как обычный термостат Вкл/Выкл или как модулирующий термостат. При работе в "модулирующем" режиме клапан будет ограничивать расход хладагента так что колебания температуры будут меньше чем в режиме двухпозиционного термостата.
Help_it:
Here it is defined how the thermostat is to operate. Either as an ordinary ON/OFF thermostat or as a modulating thermostat.
When operation is ”modulating” the valve will limit the flow of refrigerant so that the temperature variation will be less than for the ON/OFF thermostat.
The thermostat differential (r01) must not be set lower than 2K for ""modulating"".
In a decentralised plant you must select the ON/OFF thermostat setting."

Name: Differential
Help: When the temperature is higher than the set cutout + the set differential, the compressor relay will be cut in. It will cut out again when the temperature comes down to the set cutout limit
Help_en: When the temperature is higher than the set cutout + the set differential, the compressor relay will be cut in. It will cut out again when the temperature comes down to the set cutout limit
Help_zh:
当实际温度高于切断值+温度偏差时，压缩机继电器将接通。如果实际温度下降
到参考值以下时，继电器将断开.
Help_da: Indstilling af termostatens temperatur differens. Når temperaturen stiger til setpunkt + Differens vil kølingen starte. Kølingen vil stoppe igen når temperaturen når setpunktet for termostaten
Help_fr: Differentiel
Help_es: Cuando la temperatura es mayor que el valor de corte mas el diferencial, se arranca la refrigeracion. Volvera a pararse el frio cuando se llegue al valor de corte.
Help_de: When the temperature is higher than the set cutout + the set differential, the compressor relay will be cut in. It will cut out again when the temperature comes down to the set cutout limit
Help_pt: Quando a temperatura está mais alta que setpoint + diferencial, o relé do compressor irá atuar. Irá desativar novamente quando a temperatura atingir o stpoint.
Help_ru: Когда температура выше установленного значения отключения + установленный дифференциал, реле компрессора будет включено. Оно снова отключится, когда температура снизится до заданного предела отключения.
Help_it: When the temperature is higher than the set cutout + the set differential, the compressor relay will be cut in. It will cut out again when the temperature comes down to the set cutout limit

Name: Max cutout limit
Help:
Setpoint limitation - 
The controller’s setting range for the thermostat setpoint may be narrowed down, so that much too high or much too low values are not set accidentally - with resulting damages.
To avoid a too high setting of the setpoint, the max. allowable reference value may be lowered
Help_en:
Setpoint limitation - 
The controller’s setting range for the thermostat setpoint may be narrowed down, so that much too high or much too low values are not set accidentally - with resulting damages.
To avoid a too high setting of the setpoint, the max. allowable reference value may be lowered
Help_zh:
设置温度限制。需要限定控制器温控温度设置范围，避免偶然把温度设置过高或过低造成损坏。
为了避免设置温度过高，需要在此设置允许的温度设置上限。
Help_da:
Begrænsning af setpunkt for termostat. Indstillingsområdet for termostaten kan begrænses, således at man kan undgå at værdien indstilles forkert ved et uheld.
Hér indstilles den maksimale grænse for indstillingsområdet.
Help_fr: Limitation de la valeur de consigne supérieure
Help_es: Limitacion de la temperatura de corte para evitar valores incorrectos de forma accidental.
Help_de:
Setpoint limitation - 
The controller’s setting range for the thermostat setpoint may be narrowed down, so that much too high or much too low values are not set accidentally - with resulting damages.
To avoid a too high setting of the setpoint, the max. allowable reference value may be lowered
Help_pt: Limitação do setpoint - o range de ação do controlador pode ser restringido, de modo que valores inadequados não podem ser selecionado.
Help_ru: Ограничение уставки - Диапазон настроек контроллера для уставки термостата может быть заужен, таким образом слишком высокие и слишком низкие значения случайно не установить - что могло бы привести к повреждениям. Чтобы избежать слишком высоких значений уставки, максимально допустимое значение уставки может быть снижено
Help_it:
Setpoint limitation - 
The controller’s setting range for the thermostat setpoint may be narrowed down, so that much too high or much too low values are not set accidentally - with resulting damages.
To avoid a too high setting of the setpoint, the max. allowable reference value may be lowered

Чтобы избежать слишком низких значений уставки, минимально допустимое значение уставки может быть повышено

Name: Thermostat sensor S4 %
Name_zh: 温控传感器S4%柜子回路序号
Help:
Selection of thermostat sensor. 
Here you define the sensor the thermostat is to use for its control function. S3, S4, or a combination of them. 
With the setting 0%, only S3 is used. 
With 100%, only S4.
Help_en:
Selection of thermostat sensor. 
Here you define the sensor the thermostat is to use for its control function. S3, S4, or a combination of them. 
With the setting 0%, only S3 is used. 
With 100%, only S4.
Help_zh:
温控传感器选择
此处设置制冷控制的温度基准参考信号，S3、S4或S3和S4的加权。0%=S3(Sin)
，100%=S4(Sout)
Help_da:
Valg af termostat føler. Hér definerer du hvilke følere der anvendes til termostat funktionen S3, S4 eller en kombination af begge. 
Ved en indstilling på 0% anvendes udelukkende S3. Ved en indstilling på 100% anvendes udelukkende S4. Ved en indstilling imellem 1% og 99% anvendes en vægtning imellem de to følere.
Help_fr: Sélection de la sonde de régulation. Choisir la sonde entre S3, S4, ou une combinaison des 2.  0%, seul S3 est utilisé, à 100% seulement S4.
Help_es: Selección del sensor de termostato. Aqui se define el sensor que se usa para el termostato, que puede ser S3, S4 o una combinacion de ambos. Se ajusta el porcentaje de S4 y el resto seria S3. Si se quiere solo S4, seria %S4=100, si se quiere solo S3, seria %S4=0.
Help_de:
Selection of thermostat sensor. 
Here you define the sensor the thermostat is to use for its control function. S3, S4, or a combination of them. 
With the setting 0%, only S3 is used. 
With 100%, only S4.
Help_pt: Seleção do sensor para termostato. Aqui você define qual sensor será utilizado para controle do termostato. S3, S4 ou uma combinação dos dois. Com 0%, somente S3 é utilizado. Com 100% somente S4.
Help_ru: Выбор датчика термостата. Здесь Вы определяете датчик, который используется термостатом для его контрольной функции. S3, S4 или их комбинация. С настройкой 0%, используется только S3. 100%, только S4.
Help_it:
Selection of thermostat sensor. 
Here you define the sensor the thermostat is to use for its control function. S3, S4, or a combination of them. 
With the setting 0%, only S3 is used. 
With 100%, only S4.

Name: Thermostat sensor S4 % night
Help:
Selection of thermostat sensor S4% during night operation with night blinds. 
Here you define the sensor the thermostat is to use for its control function. S3, S4, or a combination of them. 
With the setting 0%, only S3 is used. 
With 100%, only S4.
Help_en:
Selection of thermostat sensor S4% during night operation with night blinds. 
Here you define the sensor the thermostat is to use for its control function. S3, S4, or a combination of them. 
With the setting 0%, only S3 is used. 
With 100%, only S4.
Help_zh:
带有夜帘控制的夜间模式下的温度加权（S4%）
在此可以定义温控所用的温度传感器基准。S3、S4或S3和S4的加权。0%=S3
，100%=S4
Help_da:
Valg af termostat føler under natdrift. Hér definerer du hvilke følere der anvendes til termostat funktionen S3, S4 eller en kombination af begge. 
Ved en indstilling på 0% anvendes udelukkende S3. Ved en indstilling på 100% anvendes udelukkende S4. Ved en indstilling imellem 1% og 99% anvendes en vægtning imellem de to følere.
Help_fr: Sélection de la sonde de régulation la nuit. Choisit la sonde entre S3, S4, ou une combinaison des 2.  0%, seul S3 est utilisé, à 100% seulement S4.
Help_es: Seleccion del %S4 en el periodo nocturno.
Help_de:
Selection of thermostat sensor S4% during night operation with night blinds. 
Here you define the sensor the thermostat is to use for its control function. S3, S4, or a combination of them. 
With the setting 0%, only S3 is used. 
With 100%, only S4.
Help_pt: Seleção do sensor termostato S4% em operação noturna com cortina. Aqui você define o sensor que o termostato irá utilizar.
Help_ru: Выбор датчика термостата S4 % во время ночного режима с ночными шторками. Здесь Вы определяете датчик, который используется термостатом для его контрольной функции. S3, S4 или их комбинация. С настройкой 0%, используется только S3. 100%, только S4.
Help_it:
Selection of thermostat sensor S4% during night operation with night blinds. 
Here you define the sensor the thermostat is to use for its control function. S3, S4, or a combination of them. 
With the setting 0%, only S3 is used. 
With 100%, only S4.

Name: Night offset
Help:
Night setback value.
The thermostat’s reference will be the setpoint plus this value when the controller changes over to night operation.
Help_en:
Night setback value.
The thermostat’s reference will be the setpoint plus this value when the controller changes over to night operation.
Help_zh: 夜间回置值，温度控制值在夜间运行时将在设定值基础上加上该值。
Help_da: Termostatens temperatur indstilling vil blive hævet med den indstillede værdi under natdrift
Help_fr: Valeur de l'offset de nuit. La référence du thermostat sera la consigne plus cette valeur quand le régulateur sera en régime de nuit.
Help_es: Ajuste Nocturno. La referencia del ternostato sera la consigna mas este valor cuando el controlador este en modo noche.
Help_de:
Night setback value.
The thermostat’s reference will be the setpoint plus this value when the controller changes over to night operation.
Help_pt: Valor para setpoint noturno. A referência do termostato será  osetpoint + este valor quando o controlador alternar para modo noturno.
Help_ru:
Значение ночного смещения.
Текущая уставка термостата будет равна заданной уставке плюс это значение, когда контроллер переключается на ночной режим работы.
Help_it:
Night setback value.
The thermostat’s reference will be the setpoint plus this value when the controller changes over to night operation.

Name: S4 frost protection
Help: Frost protection on S4 air temperature. If the S4 temperature sensors measures a temperature lower than the set limit, refrigeration will be stopped in order to protect produce from ice formation. Refrigeration will start again when the S4 temperature has risen 2K above the set limit
Help_en: Frost protection on S4 air temperature. If the S4 temperature sensors measures a temperature lower than the set limit, refrigeration will be stopped in order to protect produce from ice formation. Refrigeration will start again when the S4 temperature has risen 2K above the set limit
Help_zh: S4结霜保护功能。当检测到S4温度比设置下限要低时，控制器将停止制冷，避免结霜。当S4温度比设置下限高2K时，控制将重启。
Help_da: Frost beskyttelse på S4 luft temperaturen. Hvis S4 temperatur føleren måler en lavere temperatur end den indstillede grænse stoppes kølingen, for at beskytte de kølede varer imod frost dannelse. Kølingen genoptages når temperaturen er steget 2K over den indstillede grænse.
Help_fr: Protection anti-gel sur S4. Si la température S4 descend en dessous de la valeur réglée, la réfrigération s'arrète pour prévenir une éventuelle prise en glace. La réfrigération quand le température mesurée par S4 sera 2K au-dessus de la valeure réglée.
Help_es: Proteccion anti hielo con S4, si la temperatura de la sonda S4 es inferior al ajuste de este parametro, se para la refrigeracion para evitar la formacion de hielo. La refrigeracion empezara otra vez cuando la S4 este 2K por debajo de este limite.
Help_de: Frost protection on S4 air temperature. If the S4 temperature sensors measures a temperature lower than the set limit, refrigeration will be stopped in order to protect produce from ice formation. Refrigeration will start again when the S4 temperature has risen 2K above the set limit
Help_pt: Proteção de gelo para temperatura de ar S4. Se S4 medir uma temperatura abaixo do limite especificado, a refrigeração será interrompida. A refrigeração será retomada quando a temperatura de S4 atingir 2K acima do limite.
Help_ru: Защита от замерзания по температуре воздуха S4. Если температурный датчик S4 измеряет температуру ниже чем установленный предел, охлаждение будет остановлено, чтобы защитить продукты от образования льда. Охлаждение снова будет запущено когда температура S4 вырастет на 2К выше чем установленный предел
Help_it: Frost protection on S4 air temperature. If the S4 temperature sensors measures a temperature lower than the set limit, refrigeration will be stopped in order to protect produce from ice formation. Refrigeration will start again when the S4 temperature has risen 2K above the set limit

Name: Air heater neutral zone
Name_zh: 空气加热功能 中央区
Help:
Heat function. 
Set the width of the Neutral Zone for changeover from cooling to heating "
Help_en:
Heat function. 
Set the width of the Neutral Zone for changeover from cooling to heating "
Help_zh: 空气加热功能。设置从制冷切换到加热功能的中央区。
Help_da: Varme funktion. Sæt bredden på neutralzonen for skift imellem køling og varme
Help_fr: Fonction Chauffage. Réglage de la zone neutre entre le basculement froid chaud.
Help_es: Funcion Calor. Ajuste el ancho de la zona neutra para el cambio del modo frio al modo calor.
Help_de:
Heat function. 
Set the width of the Neutral Zone for changeover from cooling to heating "
Help_pt: Função de aquecimento. Defina a amplitude da Zona Neutra.
Help_ru: Функция нагрева. Установите ширину Нейтральной Зоны для переключения из режима охлаждения в режим нагрева
Help_it:
Heat function. 
Set the width of the Neutral Zone for changeover from cooling to heating "

Name: Air heater start delay
Help:
Time delay on transition from refrigeration phase to heating phase 
(there is not time delay on transition from heating phase to refrigeration phase)
Help_en:
Time delay on transition from refrigeration phase to heating phase 
(there is not time delay on transition from heating phase to refrigeration phase)
Help_zh: 从制冷切换到加热时的时间延迟（从加热到制冷切换时没有时间延迟）
Help_da: Tidsforsinkelse på skift imellem køle og varmefunktion (der er ingen forsinkelse i skift fra varme til køle funktion)
Help_fr: Temprisation entre le basculement du mode réfrigeration au mode chauffage (il n'y a pas de temporisation entre chauffage et refrigération)
Help_es: Retraso para cambiar el modo de refrigeracion al modo de calor. NO hay retraso para el cambio del modo calor al modo frio.
Help_de:
Time delay on transition from refrigeration phase to heating phase 
(there is not time delay on transition from heating phase to refrigeration phase)
Help_pt: Atraso de tempo na transição de refrigeração para aquecimento (não há atraso de tempo na fase de aquecimento para refrigeração).
Help_ru: Временная задержка переключения из режима охлаждения в режим нагрева (нет задержки перехода из нагрева в охлаждение)
Help_it:
Time delay on transition from refrigeration phase to heating phase 
(there is not time delay on transition from heating phase to refrigeration phase)

Name: Melt interval
Help:
Melt function. 
Only for control of MT cases/rooms (-5 to +10°C). The function ensures that the evaporator will not be blocked by ice crystals. Here you set how often the function is to stop the refrigeration and hence transform the ice crystals to water.
Help_en:
Melt function. 
Only for control of MT cases/rooms (-5 to +10°C). The function ensures that the evaporator will not be blocked by ice crystals. Here you set how often the function is to stop the refrigeration and hence transform the ice crystals to water.
Help_zh:
融霜功能
仅适用于控制温度在-5-10℃的MT柜子或冷库。该功能用于确保蒸发器不发生霜堵。在此
可以设置融霜间隔时间，用于停止制冷，将冰融化成水。
Help_da: Smelte funktionen er kun aktiv ved anvendelse på køl hvor temperaturen ligger imellem -5 to +10°C. Funktionen sikrer at fordamperen ikke bliver blokeret af iskrystaller. For hvert smelteinterval stoppes kølingen i en kort periode for at smelte de store iskrystaller imellem fordamperens finner.
Help_fr: Fonction Dégivrage. Seulement pour les evaporateur MT (-5 à +10°C). Cette fonction assure que l'éévaporateur n'est pas pris en glace. Ici vous réglez le temps entre chaque dégivrage.
Help_es: Este intervalo se usa solo para evaporadores de positiva (MT), la función asegura que el evaporador no se bloqueará de hielo. El parametro se ajusta para saber cada cuanto tiempo se debe parar la refrigeracion (el ventilador sigue funcionando).
Help_de:
Melt function. 
Only for control of MT cases/rooms (-5 to +10°C). The function ensures that the evaporator will not be blocked by ice crystals. Here you set how often the function is to stop the refrigeration and hence transform the ice crystals to water.
Help_pt: Função derretimento. Somente para sistemas MT (-5/+10°C). A função garante que o evaporador não seja bloqueado por cristais de gelo. Aqui você define a frequência de ativação dessa função para transformar os cristais em água.
Help_ru: Функция таяния. Только для СТ витрин/камер (от -5 до +10 град С). Функция предотвращает блокировку испарителя кристаллами льда. Здесь Вы определяете как часто функция останавливает охлаждение для таяния льда.
Help_it:
Melt function. 
Only for control of MT cases/rooms (-5 to +10°C). The function ensures that the evaporator will not be blocked by ice crystals. Here you set how often the function is to stop the refrigeration and hence transform the ice crystals to water.

Name: Melt period
Help:
Melt period. 
Here you set how long an on-going melt function is to last
Help_en:
Melt period. 
Here you set how long an on-going melt function is to last
Help_zh: 融霜时间。此处可设置单次融霜的持续时间。
Help_da: Smelteperiode. Hér kan du indstille længden af en smelte periode.
Help_fr: Durée max du dégivrage
Help_es: Periodo Fusion, aqui se ajusta cuanto tiempo debe estar el controlador en la funcion de fusion de escarcha.
Help_de:
Melt period. 
Here you set how long an on-going melt function is to last
Help_pt: Período de derretimento. Aqui você define qual o tempo de duração da função derretimento.
Help_ru: Период таяния. Здесь Вы устанавливаете как долго должна продолжаться функция таяния
Help_it:
Melt period. 
Here you set how long an on-going melt function is to last

Name: Alarm sensor S4% A
Help:
Signal to the alarm thermostat 
Here you have to define the ratio between the sensors which the alarm thermostat has to use. S3, S4 or a combination of the two. 

With setting 0% only S3 is used. 
With 100% only S4 is used
Help_en:
Signal to the alarm thermostat 
Here you have to define the ratio between the sensors which the alarm thermostat has to use. S3, S4 or a combination of the two. 

With setting 0% only S3 is used. 
With 100% only S4 is used
Help_zh:
报警温度加权
在此你可以定义报警温度的基准信号，S3、S4或S3和S4的加权。0%=S3，100%-S4
Help_da:
Valg af alarm føler. Hér definerer du hvilke følere der anvendes til alarm funktionen S3, S4 eller en kombination af begge. 
Ved en indstilling på 0% anvendes udelukkende S3. 
Ved en indstilling på 100% anvendes udelukkende S4. Ved en indstilling imellem 1% og 99% anvendes en vægtning imellem de to følere.
Help_fr: Signal utilisé pour l'alarme thermostat. Choisir la sonde entre S3, S4, ou une combinaison des 2.  0%, seul S3 est utilisé, à 100% seulement S4.
Help_es: Aqui se ajusta el % de la sonda S4 que se aplica a la alarma del termostato. Se puede usar el sensor S4 como alarma (100%), el S3 como alarma (0%), o bien una mezcla de ambos, Siempre se ajusta sobre la sonda S4.
Help_de:
Signal to the alarm thermostat 
Here you have to define the ratio between the sensors which the alarm thermostat has to use. S3, S4 or a combination of the two. 

With setting 0% only S3 is used. 
With 100% only S4 is used
Help_pt: Sinal para alarme do termostato. Aqui você define o peso dos sensores para ativação do alarme do termostato. S3, S4 ou uma combinação dos dois. Com 0%, somente S3 é usado. Com 100%, somente S4.
Help_ru:
Сигнал для аварийного термостата.
Здесь Вы должны определить соотношение между датчиками, которые должен использовать аварийный термостат. S3, S4 или их комбинация. При настройке 0% используется только S3. При 100% используется только S4
Help_it:
Signal to the alarm thermostat 
Here you have to define the ratio between the sensors which the alarm thermostat has to use. S3, S4 or a combination of the two. 

With setting 0% only S3 is used. 
With 100% only S4 is used

Name: High alarm limit 1
Help:
Upper alarm limit. The limit value is set in absolute value.  
The limit value will be raised with the night offset during night operation.
Help_en:
Upper alarm limit. The limit value is set in absolute value.  
The limit value will be raised with the night offset during night operation.

在此可以设定高温报警值，温度以℃为单位（绝对值）。
夜间模式下运行时，该值将会自动提高。

Name: Alarm delay A
Help:
Alarm delay (short alarm delay on air temperature)
. If the upper or the lower alarm limit values are exceeded, a timer function will commence. The alarm will not become active until the set time delay has been passed. 
The time delay is set in minutes
Help_en:
Alarm delay (short alarm delay on air temperature)
. If the upper or the lower alarm limit values are exceeded, a timer function will commence. The alarm will not become active until the set time delay has been passed. 
The time delay is set in minutes
Help_zh:
报警延时（温度短报警延时）
当实际读数超出报警最小或最大值时，将会开始计数，在时间达到设置延时后，报警将激活。该值单位为min。
Help_da: Forsinkelse for temperatur alarmer under normal drift. Hvis alarm temperaturen ligger over eller under de indstillede alarm grænser i den indstillede tid bliver der genereret en alarm
Help_fr: Temporisation sur l'apparition défaut température haut ou bas.
Help_es: Retraso de alarma de temperatura en funcionamiento normal. Si la temperatura excede del valor durante el tiempo programado, se da una alarma. El tiempo se ajusta en minutos.
Help_de:
Alarm delay (short alarm delay on air temperature)
. If the upper or the lower alarm limit values are exceeded, a timer function will commence. The alarm will not become active until the set time delay has been passed. 
The time delay is set in minutes
Help_pt: Atraso de alarme (atraso curto em temperatura do ar). Se os limites mínimos ou máximos são excedidos, uma função timer irá ativar, e o alarme somente irá acionar ao final desse atraso em minutos.
Help_ru:
Задержка аварии (короткая задержка аварии по температуре воздуха).
Если превышен верхний или нижний аварийный предел, запускается функция таймера. Авария не станет активной, пока не истечет установленное время задержки. Временная задержка устанавливается в минутах.
Help_it:
Alarm delay (short alarm delay on air temperature)
. If the upper or the lower alarm limit values are exceeded, a timer function will commence. The alarm will not become active until the set time delay has been passed. 
The time delay is set in minutes

Name: Alarm delay pulldown A
Name_ru: Задержка аварии при снижении температуры A
Help:
Alarm delay at tempeature pulldown conditions (long alarm delay). 
This time delay is used during start-up, during defrost, immediately after a defrost. There will be change-over to the normal time delay when the temperature has dropped below the set upper alarm limit.
Help_en:
Alarm delay at tempeature pulldown conditions (long alarm delay). 
This time delay is used during start-up, during defrost, immediately after a defrost. There will be change-over to the normal time delay when the temperature has dropped below the set upper alarm limit.
Help_zh:
抽空报警延时（长报警延时）
该时间延迟用于启动、除霜、除霜结束瞬间。
当温度降低到设定的高温报警值以下，会更换到正常时间延迟)。
Help_da: Forsinkelse for temperatur alarmer under nedkølingsforløb efter afrimning eller ved opstart af køling. Der skiftes til den normale tidsforsinkelse når temperaturen er kommet under den øvre alarmgrænse.
Help_fr: Temporisation de l'alarme au démarrage de l'installation.
Help_es: Retraso de alarma (largo) de temperatura cuando el controlador acaba de arrancar o esta en desescarche, El tiempo se inicia a contar dede que empieza el desescarche. Si la temperatura cae por debajo del limite fijado, entonces se cambia automaticamente al tiempo de alarma normal.s.
Help_de:
Alarm delay at tempeature pulldown conditions (long alarm delay). 
This time delay is used during start-up, during defrost, immediately after a defrost. There will be change-over to the normal time delay when the temperature has dropped below the set upper alarm limit.
Help_pt: Atraso de alarme em condições de pulldown.
Help_ru: Задержка аварии в условиях снижения температуры (длительная задержка аварии). Эта временная задержка используется во время запуска, во время оттайки, сразу после оттайки. Когда температура упадет ниже установленного верхнего предела аварии, произойдет переход к нормальной задержке.
Help_it:
Alarm delay at tempeature pulldown conditions (long alarm delay).

Help:
MOP temperature. The valve opening degree is reduced until the evaporating temperature reaches the set MOP limit. 
If no MOP function is required, select highest value, which corresponds to OFF
Help_en:
MOP temperature. The valve opening degree is reduced until the evaporating temperature reaches the set MOP limit. 
If no MOP function is required, select highest value, which corresponds to OFF
Help_zh:
MOP温度
当蒸发温度比MOP温度高时，阀开启度将减小。当不需要MOP温度控制时，把该值设成最大。
Help_da: MOP temperatur. Ventilens åbningsgrad begrænses indtil fordampningstemperaturen når ned på den indstillede værdi. Indstil til højeste værdi hvis funktionen ikke skal anvendes
Help_fr: Temp. MOP. Le degré d'ouverture de la vanne se réduit tant que la température d'évaporation n'atteint pas la valeur limit MOP. Si pas de fonction MOP requise, la valeur la plus haute correspond à OFF.
Help_es: Presion MOP. El grado de apertura de la valvula se reducira hasta que la presion de evaporacion alcance el limite ajustado en MOP y este por debajo de este. SI no se quiere usar MOP, ajustar este parametro al maximo valor.
Help_de:
MOP temperature. The valve opening degree is reduced until the evaporating temperature reaches the set MOP limit. 
If no MOP function is required, select highest value, which corresponds to OFF

Help: When the selected defrost stop sensor reaches the set limit, the defrost cycle is terminated
Help_en: When the selected defrost stop sensor reaches the set limit, the defrost cycle is terminated
Help_zh: 当选择的除霜停止温度探头读数达到设定值，除霜将停止
Help_da: Indstil ved hvilken temperatur en afrimning skal afsluttes. Når den valgte afrimningsstopføler når den indstillede værdi afsluttes afrimningen.
Help_fr: Quand la sonde de fin de dégivrage atteint le seuil, le cycle de dégivrage s'arrete.
Help_es: Cuando la sonda seleccionada alcanza este limite de temperatura, el desescahe finaliza.
Help_de: When the selected defrost stop sensor reaches the set limit, the defrost cycle is terminated
Help_pt: Quando o sensor estipulado para o degelo atinge este limite, o ciclo de degelo é finalizado
Help_ru: Когда выбранный датчик остановки оттайки достигнет установленного предела, цикл оттайки прекратится
Help_it: When the selected defrost stop sensor reaches the set limit, the defrost cycle is terminated

Name: Max defrost time
Help: Max duration of a defrost cycle. The setting is also used as a safety time if the defrost is stopped on temperature. If the selected defrost stop sensor does not reach the set defrost stop temperature limit within the set time, the defrost will be stopped anyway.
Help_en: Max duration of a defrost cycle. The setting is also used as a safety time if the defrost is stopped on temperature. If the selected defrost stop sensor does not reach the set defrost stop temperature limit within the set time, the defrost will be stopped anyway.
Help_zh:
单次除霜最大持续时间
改参数也用于除霜按照温度停止时的安全时间。当选择的除霜温度探头在当前设置时间后仍未能达到设定温度时，除霜依然会停止。
Help_da: Maksimal varighed af en afrimning. Hvis afrimning er sat til at stoppe på temperatur, vil den blive stoppet hvis tiden overskrider den indstillede tid
Help_fr: Durée maximal d'un cycle de dégivrage. Le paramètre sert également de sécurité lors de dégivrage avec arret sur seuil de température. Si la température réglée n'est pas atteinte avant la fin de Temps max Deg. Le dégivrage s'arrète.
Help_es: Maximo tiempo de un ciclo de desescarche. El ajuste se usa tambien como una funcion de seguridad, si la sonda de desescarche seleccionada no llega al valor de fin de desescarche en el tiempo requerido, entonces el desescarche se finaliza.
Help_de: Max duration of a defrost cycle. The setting is also used as a safety time if the defrost is stopped on temperature. If the selected defrost stop sensor does not reach the set defrost stop temperature limit within the set time, the defrost will be stopped anyway.
Help_pt: Duração máxima de um ciclo de degelo. Este parâmetro é usado também como segurança se o degelo for finalizado por temperatura. Se o sensor designado para o degello não atingir a temperatura, o degelo será finalizado por este tempo.
Help_ru: Максимальная продолжительность цикла оттайки. Этот параметр также является защитным временем, усли оттайка останавливается по температуре. Если выбранный датчик остановки оттайки не достиг установленной предельной температуры остановки оттайки в течение установленного времени, оттайка в любом случае прекратится.
Help_it: Max duration of a defrost cycle. The setting is also used as a safety time if the defrost is stopped on temperature. If the selected defrost stop sensor does not reach the set defrost stop temperature limit within the set time, the defrost will be stopped anyway.

Name: Defrost start interval
Help:
The function is zeroset and will start the timer function at each defrost start. When the time has expired the function will start a defrost. 
The function is used as a simple defrost start, or it may be used as a safeguard if the normal signal fails to appear. 
If master/slave defrost without clock function or without data communication is used, the interval time will be used as max. time between defrosts. 
If a defrost start via data communcation does not take place, the interval time will be used as max. time between defrosts.
When there is defrost with clock function or data communication, the interval time must be set for a somewhat longer period of time than the planned one.  In connection with power failure the interval time will be maintained, and when the power returns the interval time will continue from the maintained value. 
he interval time is not active when set to 0
Help_en:
The function is zeroset and will start the timer function at each defrost start. When the time has expired the function will start a defrost. 
The function is used as a simple defrost start, or it may be used as a safeguard if the normal signal fails to appear. 
If master/slave defrost without clock function or without data communication is used, the interval time will be used as max. time between defrosts. 
If a defrost start via data communcation does not take place, the interval time will be used as max. time between defrosts.
When there is defrost with clock function or data communication, the interval time must be set for a somewhat longer period of time than the planned one.  In connection with power failure the interval time will be maintained, and when the power returns the interval time will continue from the maintained value. 
he interval time is not active when set to 0
Help_zh:
该功能带有清零功能，并在每次除霜启动后启动计时器功能。当时间已过，该功能启动除霜。该功能被作为一种简单的除霜启动，或者当接收不到正常的信号时用作安全措
施。
如果主/从除霜没有使用计时功能或者没有使用数据传输，时间间隔将被用作两次
除霜之间的最长时间。
如果通过数据传输启动除霜没能实现，时间间隔将被用作两次除霜之间的最长时间。
当除霜带有计时功能或者数据传输时，间隔时间的设置应当比原计划的时间要长一些，因为间隔时间会再启动一个除霜，该除霜紧随原计划的除霜后面进行。
断电后间隔时间会被保存，当供电恢复后间隔时间从保存的时间继续。
如果时间间隔设为0将不被启动。
Help_da: Maksimalt tidsinterval imellem to afrimninger. Hvis regulatoren ikke har udført en afrimning inden for det indstillede tidsinterval, vil der automatisk blive startet en afrimning.Hvis der anvendes et afrimningstidsskema skal værdien stilles til en højere værdi end den længste tidsperiode imellem to afrimninger i tidsskemaet
Help_fr:
Intervalle entre le début du dégivrage
La fonction est définie sur zéro et lancera la fonction de minuterie à chaque démarrage du dégivrage.
Help_es: La funcion se pone a cero cuando se inicia un desescarche y empieza a contar el tiempo. Cuando llega al tiempo definido se inicia un desescarche (independientemente de que se usen otros metodos para iniciar el desescarche). Esta funcion se puede usar como horario de desescarche o bien como una seguridad de que cada X tiempo se van a hacer desescarches (siempre y cuando no se hayan iniciado por otros metodos)
Help_de:
The function is zeroset and will start the timer function at each defrost start. When the time has expired the function will start a defrost. 
The function is used as a simple defrost start, or it may be used as a safeguard if the normal signal fails to appear. 
If master/slave defrost without clock function or without data communication is used, the interval time will be used as max. time between defrosts. 
If a defrost start via data communcation does not take place, the interval time will be used as max. time between defrosts.
When there is defrost with clock function or data communication, the interval time must be set for a somewhat longer period of time than the planned one.  In connection with power failure the interval time will be maintained, and when the power returns the interval time will continue from the maintained value. 
he interval time is not active when set to 0
Help_pt: Esta função irá zerar a contagem de tempo após a ativação do degelo. Quando o tempo expirar, u mdegelo irá iniciar. Esta função pdoe ser usada como degelo normal ou segurança, caso o sinal de degelo não chegue por comunicação.
Help_ru: Функция имеет нулевое значение и будет запускать функцию таймера при каждом запуске оттайки. Когда время истекло, функция начнет оттайку. Функция применяется для простого запуска оттайки, или она может использоваться для безопасности, если обычный сигнал не поступил.

he interval time is not active when set to 0

Name: Time staggering power up
Name_es: Decalado de tiempo al dar tension
Help:
Time staggering for defrost cutins during start-up 
The function is only relevant if you have several refrigeration appliances or groups where you want the defrost to be staggered in relation to one another. The function is furthermore only relevant if you have chosen defrost with interval start. The function delays the interval time by the set number of minutes, but it only does it once, and this at the very first defrost taking place when voltage is connected to the controller. 
The function will be active after each and every power failure.
Help_en:
Time staggering for defrost cutins during start-up 
The function is only relevant if you have several refrigeration appliances or groups where you want the defrost to be staggered in relation to one another. The function is furthermore only relevant if you have chosen defrost with interval start. The function delays the interval time by the set number of minutes, but it only does it once, and this at the very first defrost taking place when voltage is connected to the controller. 
The function will be active after each and every power failure.
Help_zh:
启动时化霜的交错运行
如果你有几个或者机组制冷设备，并且希望除霜能够互相交错开始，才使用该功
能。如果你已经选择间隔时间除霜(d03)，也会使用该功能。该功能将时间间隔延
迟设定的几分钟，但只延迟一次，并且在控制器通电后的第一次除霜进行。
每次断电后该功能被激活。
Help_da: Forskydning af afrimning efter opstart af regulator. Funktionen er kun relevant hvis man har mange kølemøbler og man anvender afrimningsinterval timeren til at starte afrimninger. Med tidsforskydningen kan man fordele den elektrisk belastning fra afrimningerne efter en opstart fra et strømudfald.
Help_fr:
Temps de décalage pour les enclenchementde dégivrage lors du démarrage
La fonction n'est utile que si vous avez plusieurs appareils de réfrigération ou groupes pour lesquels vous souhaitez que le dégivrage soit échelonné.
Help_es: Decalado de tiempo para separar los desescarches entre varios controladores al dar tension a los equipos.
Help_de:
Time staggering for defrost cutins during start-up 
The function is only relevant if you have several refrigeration appliances or groups where you want the defrost to be staggered in relation to one another. The function is furthermore only relevant if you have chosen defrost with interval start. The function delays the interval time by the set number of minutes, but it only does it once, and this at the very first defrost taking place when voltage is connected to the controller. 
The function will be active after each and every power failure.
Help_pt: Tempo de estágios para início de degelo ao iniciar. Função útil apenas em caso de várias aplicações de refrigeração ou grupos onde deseja-se o degelo em estágios, com relação aos outros.
Help_ru: Смещение по времени при запуске. Эта функция актуальна только в том случае, если у вас есть несколько холодильных устройств или групп, в которых вы хотите, чтобы размораживание было в шахматном порядке относительно друг друга. Функция также актуальна, если выбран запуск оттайки с интервалом.
Help_it:
Time staggering for defrost cutins during start-up

The function is furthermore only relevant if you have chosen defrost with interval start. The function delays the interval time by the set number of minutes, but it only does it once, and this at the very first defrost taking place when voltage is connected to the controller. 
The function will be active after each and every power failure.

Name: Max thermostat runtime
Name_pt: Tempo max de funcionamento do termostato
Help:
Defrost on demand – aggregate refrigeration time 
Set here is the refrigeration time allowed without defrosts. If the time is passed, a defrost will be started. With setting = 0 the function is not in use.
Help_en:
Defrost on demand – aggregate refrigeration time 
Set here is the refrigeration time allowed without defrosts. If the time is passed, a defrost will be started. With setting = 0 the function is not in use.
Help_zh:
按需除霜-制冷时间累积
在没有除霜的情况下允许制冷的时间。如果设定时间已经过去，控制器会启动一
次除霜。设定值=0，功能禁用。
Help_da: Behovsafrimning baseret på termostatens  akkumulerede køretid. Når den akkumulerede køretid når den indstillede værdi startes en afrimning. Ved at indstille værdien til "0" bliver funktionen deaktiveret
Help_fr: Degivrage à la demande - temps de réfrigération cumulé. Le temps de réfrigération autorisé sans dégivrage est défini ici. Si le temps est passé, un dégivrage sera lancé. Réglage = 0 la fonction n'est pas utilisée.
Help_es: Desescarche bajo demanda - Se suma el tiempo acumulado de refrigeracion que puede haber sin desescarches, si el tiempo es mayor que el ajuste de este parametro se inicia un desescarche. Con el ajuste en 0, no se usa.
Help_de:
Defrost on demand – aggregate refrigeration time 
Set here is the refrigeration time allowed without defrosts. If the time is passed, a defrost will be started. With setting = 0 the function is not in use.
Help_pt: Degelo em demanda - agregar tempo de refrigeração. Defina aqui o tempo máximo de refrigeração permitido sem degelos. Se este tempo for excedido, um degelo será iniciado. Com o parâmetro em 0, a função está desabilitada.
Help_ru: Оттайка по необходимости - время наработки охлаждения. Установите здесь время работы охлаждения без оттаек. По истечении времени будет запущена оттайка. С настройкой =0 функция не используется.
Help_it:
Defrost on demand – aggregate refrigeration time 
Set here is the refrigeration time allowed without defrosts. If the time is passed, a defrost will be started. With setting = 0 the function is not in use.

Name: Pump down delay
Help: Set the time where the evaporator is emptied of refrigerant prior to the actual defrost cycle
Help_en: Set the time where the evaporator is emptied of refrigerant prior to the actual defrost cycle
Help_zh: 在实际输出开始之前，蒸发器放空制冷剂的时间
Help_da: Tid for tømning af fordamper, hvor ventilen holdes lukket og fordamperen tømmes for kølemiddel
Help_fr: Tempo Pump Down
Help_es: Ajuste del tiempo en el que se vacia el evaporador antes de iniciar un ciclo de desescarche.
Help_de: Set the time where the evaporator is emptied of refrigerant prior to the actual defrost cycle
Help_pt: Defina o tempo que o evaporador será esvaziado de refrigerante antes do cicl ode degelo
Help_ru: Настройка времени опустошения испарителя от хладагента перед циклом оттайки
Help_it: Set the time where the evaporator is emptied of refrigerant prior to the actual defrost cycle

Name: Drip off time
Help: Here you set the time that is to elapse from a defrost and until the compressor is to start again. (The time when water drips off the evaporator).
Help_en: Here you set the time that is to elapse from a defrost and until the compressor is to start again. (The time when water drips off the evaporator).
Help_zh: 设定化霜结束后到压缩机再次起动的的时间（水从蒸发器上流下的时间）
Help_da: Instilling af tidsforsinkelse efter afrimningen, hvor vandet drypper af fordamperen indtil kølingen startes igen
Help_fr: Tempo Egouttage
Help_es: Tiempo que pasa desde que finaliza el desescarche y el evaporador arranca el frio otra vez. (el tiempo que se necesita para que las gotas caigan del evaporador).
Help_de: Here you set the time that is to elapse from a defrost and until the compressor is to start again. (The time when water drips off the evaporator).
Help_pt: Definição do tempo entre o final do degelo e início do compressor (o tempo que a água goteja do evaporador).
Help_ru: Здесь Вы устанавливаете время, которое должно пройти с момента оттайки до запуска компрессора. (Время когда вода удалится с испарителя)
Help_it: Here you set the time that is to elapse from a defrost and until the compressor is to start again. (The time when water drips off the evaporator).

Name: Max hold time
Help:
Max. standby time after coordinated defrost. 
When a controller has completed a defrost it will wait for a signal which tells that the refrigeration may be resumed. If this signal fails to appear for one reason or another, the controller will itself start the refrigeration when this standby time has elapsed.
Help_en:
Max. standby time after coordinated defrost. 
When a controller has completed a defrost it will wait for a signal which tells that the refrigeration may be resumed. If this signal fails to appear for one reason or another, the controller will itself start the refrigeration when this standby time has elapsed.
Help_zh: 在协同化霜模式下，单台柜子化霜完成后的最大等待时间。当控制器完成化霜后，需要接收信号才会开始制冷。当在等待时间内没有接收到其它控制器或主控器的信号时，控制器将开始制冷。
Help_da: Maksimal ventetid efter en koordineret afrimning. Efter en koordineret afrimning startes køling først når alle fordampere har afsluttet afrimningen. Hvis alle fordampere ikke når at blive færdige inden den indstillede ventetid startes kølingen under alle omstændigheder
Help_fr: Maintien Max après une coordination de dégivrage. la temposrisation démarre lorsqu'un régulateur termine sont dégivrage. Lorsque cette temporisation est écoulée, tous les régulateurs coordonnés repartent en froid.
Help_es: Maximo tiempo de espera en el que el controlador espera a los demas evaporadores que estan en desescarche coordinado. Si la señal falla por alguna razon, el controlador iniciara la refrigeracion cuando se cumpla este tiempo.
Help_de:
Max. standby time after coordinated defrost. 
When a controller has completed a defrost it will wait for a signal which tells that the refrigeration may be resumed. If this signal fails to appear for one reason or another, the controller will itself start the refrigeration when this standby time has elapsed.
Help_pt: Tempo máx standby após degelo coordenado. Quando o controlador completou o degelo, ele irá aguardar pelo sinal que a refrigeração pode reiniciar. Se o sinal não for recebido, o controlador irá iniciar a refrigeração quando este tempo for atingido.
Help_ru: Максимальное время ожидания после координированной оттайки. Когда контроллер завершил оттайку, он будет ждать сигнал, который сообщит, что охлаждение может быть продолжено. Если этот сигнал не пришел по той или иной причине, контроллер самостоятельно начнет охлаждение по истечении этого времени ожидания
Help_it:
Max. standby time after coordinated defrost. 
When a controller has completed a defrost it will wait for a signal which tells that the refrigeration may be resumed. If this signal fails to appear for one reason or another, the controller will itself start the refrigeration when this standby time has elapsed.

Name: Fan control during defrost
Help:
Fan operation during defrost 
Here you can set how the fan is to operate during defrost.

0: Stopped (Runs during pump down)


1: Running (stopped during  "fan delay")
2: Running during pump down and defrost. After that stopped


3: Running during pump down and defrost until defrost stop sensor reaches fan stop temperature limit
Help_en:
Fan operation during defrost 
Here you can set how the fan is to operate during defrost.

0: Stopped (Runs during pump down)


1: Running (stopped during  "fan delay")
2: Running during pump down and defrost. After that stopped


3: Running during pump down and defrost until defrost stop sensor reaches fan stop temperature limit
Help_zh:
除霜中风机运行
此处可设置在除霜中风机的运行状态
0：停止（在抽空过程依然运行）；1：运行（在"风机启动延时"中停止）；2：在抽空和除霜中运行，然后停止；3：在抽空和除霜中运行，直到除霜停止温度达到风机停止温度。
Help_da:
Vælg hvordan blæseren skal styres under en afrimning

0: Blæseren er stoppet


1: Blæser kører, men er stoppet under blæserforsinkelse

2: Blæser kører, men stopper ved afdrypning


3: Blæser kører, men stopper når den valgte afrimningsstopføler når temperaturgrænse for blæser stop
Help_fr:
Ventilation en marche pendant le dégivrage
Ici, vous pouvez définir si le ventilateur doit fonctionner pendant le dégivrage.0:Arret (Marche durant le Pump Down)2: Marche (arret durant "tempo ventil)2: Marche durant Pump Down et degivrage. arret ensuite3: Marche pendant Pump Down et degivrage jusqu'a ce que la temperature arret ventil soit atteinte.
Help_es:
Ajuste del funcionamiento del ventilador durante el desescarche.
0 = Parado (funciona en el tiempo de vaciado)
1 = En marcha (se para en el tiempo de retraso ventiladores)
2 = En marcha en el vaciado y en desescarche, pero luego se para.
3 = En marcha en el vaciado y en el desescarche hasta que el sensor de temperatura de fin de desescarche alcanza el limite de paro de ventiladores.
Help_de:
Fan operation during defrost 
Here you can set how the fan is to operate during defrost.

0: Stopped (Runs during pump down)


1: Running (stopped during  "fan delay")
2: Running during pump down and defrost. After that stopped


3: Running during pump down and defrost until defrost stop sensor reaches fan stop temperature limit
Help_pt: Operação do ventialdor durante o degelo. 0: parado (funciona em pump down), 1: funcionando (parado durante "atraso do ventilador"), 2: funcionando durante pump down e degelo. Parado após isso, 3: funcionando duranet pump down e degelo até o sensor de final de degelo atingir a temperatura para parar o ventilador
Help_ru: Работа вентилятора во время оттайки. Здесь можно выбрать как работает вентилятор во время оттайки. 0: Остановлен (работает во время откачки), 1: Работает (остановлен во время "задержки вентилятора"), 2: Работает во время откачки и оттайки. После чего остановлен, 3: Работает во время откачки и оттайки пока датчик оттайки не достиг предела остановки вентилятора.
Help_it:
Fan operation during defrost 
Here you can set how the fan is to operate during defrost.

0: Stopped (Runs during pump down)


1: Running (stopped during  "fan delay")
2: Running during pump down and defrost. After that stopped


3: Running during pump down and defrost until defrost stop sensor reaches fan stop temperature limit

Name: Fan start delay
Help:
Delay of fan start after defrost. 
Here you set the time that is to elapse from compressor start after a defrost and until the fan may start again. (The time when remaining water is transformed into ice on the evaporator).
Help_en:
Delay of fan start after defrost. 
Here you set the time that is to elapse from compressor start after a defrost and until the fan may start again. (The time when remaining water is transformed into ice on the evaporator).
Help_zh:
除霜后风机启动延时
此处可设置除霜后，压缩机启动到风机启动前的时间（留在蒸发器上的水结冰的时间）
Help_da: Forsinkelse på opstart af blæser efter afrimning
Help_fr: Delai avant le démarrage de la ventilation après un dégivrage.
Help_es: Retraso arranque de ventiladores.
Help_de:
Delay of fan start after defrost. 
Here you set the time that is to elapse from compressor start after a defrost and until the fan may start again. (The time when remaining water is transformed into ice on the evaporator).
Help_pt: Atraso do ventilador após finalizar o degelo.
Help_ru: Задержка запуска вентилятора после оттайки. Здесь Вы устанавливаете время, которое должно пройти от запуска компрессора после оттайки и до тех пор, пока вентилятор не запустится снова. (Время, когда оставшаяся вода примерзнет к испарителю).
Help_it:
Delay of fan start after defrost. 
Here you set the time that is to elapse from compressor start after a defrost and until the fan may start again. (The time when remaining water is transformed into ice on the evaporator).

Name: Fan start temperature
Help: Temperature limit for starting the fans after a defrost. When the measured S5 evaporator temperature is getting below the set limit, the fans are started
Help_en: Temperature limit for starting the fans after a defrost. When the measured S5 evaporator temperature is getting below the set limit, the fans are started
Help_zh:
除霜后风机启动温度限制
除霜后，当S5化霜温度比设定值小，风机将启动
Help_da: Temperaturgrænse for opstart af blæser efter afrimning. Når fordamperføleren kommer under den indstillede temperatur, vil blæseren starte (det tilbageværende vand på fordamperen vil være frosset til is)
Help_fr: Temperature S5 limite apres laquelle la ventilation démarre suite à un dégivrage.
Help_es: Limite de temperatura para el arranque de los ventiladores despues de un desescarche. Cuando la sonda S5 del evaporador este por debajo de este valor, los ventiladores arrancaran.
Help_de: Temperature limit for starting the fans after a defrost. When the measured S5 evaporator temperature is getting below the set limit, the fans are started
Help_pt: Limite de temperatura para acionamento dos ventiladores após o degelo. Quando o sensor S5  medir uma temperatura abaixo do limite, os ventiladores acionam.
Help_ru: Температурный предел для запуска вентиляторов после оттайки. Когда измеренная S5 температура испарителя станет ниже установленного предела, вентиляторы запустятся
Help_it: Temperature limit for starting the fans after a defrost. When the measured S5 evaporator temperature is getting below the set limit, the fans are started

Name: Fan stop temperature
Help: If the fan control during defrost has been set up for it, the fans can be stopped during the defrost if the defrost sensor exceeds the set temperature limit
Help_en: If the fan control during defrost has been set up for it, the fans can be stopped during the defrost if the defrost sensor exceeds the set temperature limit
Help_zh: 如果除霜中风机运行，当化霜温度超出设定值后风机将停止。
Help_da: Hvis blæserstyringen under afrimning er sat op til det, kan blæseren stoppes når den valgte afrimningsstopføler når den indstillede temperaturgrænse
Help_fr: Temperature Arret Ventil.
Help_es: Si el control de ventiladores se ha ajustado para que se paren durante el desescarche entonces se pararan si el sensor de desescarche excede el limite de temperatura.
Help_de: If the fan control during defrost has been set up for it, the fans can be stopped during the defrost if the defrost sensor exceeds the set temperature limit
Help_pt: Se o controle do ventilador durante o degelo foi habilitado, os ventiladores podem ser parados durante o degelo se o sensor de degelo exceder o limite de temperatura
Help_ru: Если управление вентилятором во время оттайки настроено на это, вентиляторы могут быть остановлены во время оттайки если датчик оттайки превысил установленный температурный предел
Help_it: If the fan control during defrost has been set up for it, the fans can be stopped during the defrost if the defrost sensor exceeds the set temperature limit

Name: Rail heat during defrost
Help:
Define how railheat is controlled during defrost

0: Railheat is OFF all the time

1: Railheat is ON all the time

2: Normal railheat control
Help_en:
Define how railheat is controlled during defrost

0: Railheat is OFF all the time

1: Railheat is ON all the time

2: Normal railheat control
Help_zh:
设定除霜中防结露是否允许
0：防结露不运行；
1：防结露一直允许；
2：正常防结露控制
Help_da:
Vælg hvordan kantvarmen skal styres under afrimning:

0: Kantvarme er slukket

1: Kantvarme er tændt hele tiden

2: Den normale kantvarme styring fortsætter uændret
Help_fr: Rail antibuée pendant le dégivrage 0=OFF. 1=ON. 2=À impulsions
Help_es:
Definir como tiene que controlarse el antivaho durante el desescarche. 
0: El antivaho esta OFF siempre
1: Antivaho esta ON todo el tiempo
2: Control antivaho normal.
Help_de:
Define how railheat is controlled during defrost

0: Railheat is OFF all the time

1: Railheat is ON all the time

2: Normal railheat control
Help_pt: Defina como o desembaçador irá atuar durante o degelo. 0: Desemb. está OFF todo o tempo; 1: Desemb. está ligado todo o tempo; 2: Controle normal do desembaçador.
Help_ru: Определяет как управлять кантовым подогревом во время оттайки. 0: Кантовый подогрев ВЫКЛ все время. 1: Кантовый подогрев ВКЛ все время. 2: Обычное управление кантовым подогревом
Help_it:
Define how railheat is controlled during defrost

0: Railheat is OFF all the time

1: Railheat is ON all the time

2: Normal railheat control

Name: Display delay after defrost
Help: Set the maximum time the display should show the defrost code "-d-" after a defrost. The normal temperature readout is normally started when the temperature in the case is OK again or if a high temperature alarm is raised.
Help_en: Set the maximum time the display should show the defrost code "-d-" after a defrost. The normal temperature readout is normally started when the temperature in the case is OK again or if a high temperature alarm is raised.
Help_zh:
设置除霜后显示"-d-"的最大持续时间。
通常除霜后在温度降低到设定值或高温报警时才会显示温度。
Help_da: Indstil den maksimale tid displayet vil vise koden "-d-" efter en afrimning. Der skiftes til normal temperatur visning i displayet når temperaturen er OK igen eller hvis der udløses en høj temperatur alarm
Help_fr: Temps maximal a réglé pour l'affichage du "-d-" après un dégivrage.
Help_es: Ajuste del maximo tiempo que se mostrara una -d- en el display para evitar ver una temperatura alta despues del desescarche.
Help_de: Set the maximum time the display should show the defrost code "-d-" after a defrost. The normal temperature readout is normally started when the temperature in the case is OK again or if a high temperature alarm is raised.
Help_pt: Defina o tempo máximo em que o código -d- é mostrado no display após o degelo. A leitura normal de temperatura é retomada no display quando o controlador atinge a tmperatura de setpoint, ou se um alarme de alta temperatura é ativado.
Help_ru: Установите максимальное время, в течение которого дисплей должен показывать код оттайки "-d-" после оттайки. Показания нормальной температуры начнутся когда температура в витрине будет в норме или если возникнет авария высокой температуры.
Help_it: Set the maximum time the display should show the defrost code "-d-" after a defrost. The normal temperature readout is normally started when the temperature in the case is OK again or if a high temperature alarm is raised.

Name: Delay between comp.
Help:
Time delay for couplings of two compressors. 
The step delay is the time that has to elapse from the first compressor cuts in and until the next compressor can cut in.
Help_en:
Time delay for couplings of two compressors. 
The step delay is the time that has to elapse from the first compressor cuts in and until the next compressor can cut in.
Help_zh:
两台压缩机之间的加载运行间隔。
第一台压缩机运行后，第二台压缩机启动前需要等待的时间。
Help_da: Tidsforsinkelse imellem start af to kompressorer
Help_fr: Tempo entre l'enclenchement de 2 compresseurs
Help_es: Retraso de tiempo para arrancar compresores. Este retraso es el tiempo que tiene que pasar desde que arranca el primer compresor y hasta que se puede arrancar el siguiente.
Help_de:
Time delay for couplings of two compressors. 
The step delay is the time that has to elapse from the first compressor cuts in and until the next compressor can cut in.
Help_pt: Atraso para acionamento entre compressores
Help_ru: Задержка для включения двух компрессоров. Задержка шага это время которое должно пройти от включения первого компрессора и до включения следующего компрессора.
Help_it:
Time delay for couplings of two compressors. 
The step delay is the time that has to elapse from the first compressor cuts in and until the next compressor can cut in.

Name: Step control mode
Help:
Selection of step control mode for compressors. 
At sequential mode compressor 1 will always be the first to start and the last to stop. 
In cyclic mode the run time between the compressor will be equalized.
Help_en:
Selection of step control mode for compressors. 
At sequential mode compressor 1 will always be the first to start and the last to stop. 
In cyclic mode the run time between the compressor will be equalized.
Help_zh:
选择压缩机的加载控制模式。
选择顺序模式时，压缩机1将第一台开启，第一台关闭，选择循环模式时，将按照运行时间优先启动和关闭压缩机。
Help_da:
Valg af koblingsmetode for kompressorer. 
Ved sekventiel drift startes kompressor 1 altid først og stoppes sidst. 
Ved cyklisk drift foretages drift time udligning imellem kompressorerne
Help_fr: Mode Etage, séquentiel ou cyclique
Help_es: Seleccion del modo de control de compresores. El modo secuencial implica que el compresor numero 1 siempre es el primero en arrancar y parar. El el modo ciclico, se igualan tiempos de funcionamiento entre los compresores.
Help_de:
Selection of step control mode for compressors. 
At sequential mode compressor 1 will always be the first to start and the last to stop. 
In cyclic mode the run time between the compressor will be equalized.
Help_pt: Seleção de modalidade de controle de passos para compressores. No modo sequencial o compressor 1 será sempre o primeiro a iniciar. No modo cíclico, as horas de trabalho entre os compressores serão equalizadas.
Help_ru: Выбор шагового режима управления для компрессоров. При последовательном режиме компрессор 1 будет всегда первым запускаться и последним останавливаться. При циклическом режиме время работы двух компрессоров будет выравниваться.
Help_it:
Selection of step control mode for compressors. 
At sequential mode compressor 1 will always be the first to start and the last to stop. 
In cyclic mode the run time between the compressor will be equalized.
