Name: Fan stop high S5 temp.
Name_es: Paro Vent con alta temp S5
Name_ru: Остановка вентилятора при высокой темп S5
Help:
Fan stop temperature 
The function stops the fans in an error situation, so that they will not provide power to the appliance. If the defrost sensor registers a higher temperature than the one set here, the fans will be stopped. There will be re-start at 2 K below the setting. 
The function is not active during a defrost or start-up after a defrost.
Help_en:
Fan stop temperature 
The function stops the fans in an error situation, so that they will not provide power to the appliance. If the defrost sensor registers a higher temperature than the one set here, the fans will be stopped. There will be re-start at 2 K below the setting. 
The function is not active during a defrost or start-up after a defrost.
Help_zh:
风机停止温度
该功能在错误情况下停止风机，这样风机就不会给设备提供动力。如果除霜传感器测量到一个比该设定的温度还高的温度，风扇就会停止。当温度比设定温度低2K时风扇才会重启。
该功能在除霜或者除霜以后的启动期间不起作用。
当设定值为+50℃时该功能被中断。
Help_da:
Funktionen stopper ventilatorerne i en fejlsituation, så de ikke tilfører effekt til kølestedet.
Hvis afrimningsføleren registrerer en højere temperatur end den her indstillede,
bliver ventilatorerne stoppet. Der startes igen 2 K under indstillingen.
Funktionen er ikke aktiv under en afrimning eller ved opstart efter en afrimning.
Help_fr:
Température d’arrêt du ventilateur En cas d’erreur de fonctionnement, cette fonction arrête les ventilateurs pour qu’ils n’apportent pas de puissance au meuble frigorifique. Si la sonde de dégivrage enregistre une température dépassant ce réglage, les ventilateurs sont arrêtés. Ils sont redémarrés à 2 K sous le réglage. Cette fonction n’est pas active en cours de dégivrage ou de démarrage après un dégivrage.
Avec le réglage +50°C, la fonction est coupée.
Help_es: Paro ventilador por temperatura. La funcion para el ventilador en caso de fallo. Si el sensor de desescarche registra una mayor temperatura que lo ajustado aqui, el ventilador se para. Hay un re-inicio a 2K por debajo del ajuste. La funcion no esta activa en desescarche o despues de un desescarche.
Help_de:
Fan stop temperature 
The function stops the fans in an error situation, so that they will not provide power to the appliance. If the defrost sensor registers a higher temperature than the one set here, the fans will be stopped. There will be re-start at 2 K below the setting. 
The function is not active during a defrost or start-up after a defrost.
Help_pt: Temperatura de parada do ventilador. A função para o ventilador em caso de aplicação equivocada. Se o sensor de degelo registra uma temperatura mais alta do que a definida aqui, os ventiladores irão parar. O ventialdor irá reiniciar em 2K abaixo do valor. A função não está ativa durante um degelo ou acionamento após degelo.
Help_ru: Температура остановки вентилятора. Функция останавливает вентиляторы в ситуации аварии, так что они не поставляют энергию в устройство. Если датчик оттайки регистрирует более высокую температуру чем установлена здесь, вентиляторы будут остановлены. Повторный запуск произойдет при 2К ниже настройки.
Help_it:
Fan stop temperature 
The function stops the fans in an error situation, so that they will not provide power to the appliance. If the defrost sensor registers a higher temperature than the one set here, the fans will be stopped. There will be re-start at 2 K below the setting. 
The function is not active during a defrost or start-up after a defrost.

Name: Rail heat control mode
Help:
The rail heat can be controlled in several ways: 


0: Railheat is running all the time 


1: Pulse control is used with a timer function following the day/night operation 


2: Pulse control is used with a dew point function. This function requires that a signal is received about the dew point value. The value is measured by a system manager and sent to the controller via the data communication.
Help_en:
The rail heat can be controlled in several ways: 


0: Railheat is running all the time 


1: Pulse control is used with a timer function following the day/night operation 


2: Pulse control is used with a dew point function. This function requires that a signal is received about the dew point value. The value is measured by a system manager and sent to the controller via the data communication.
Help_zh:
防结霜加热可以通过以下几种方式控制：
0：防露加热一致运行；
1：在白天和夜间运行中，按照计时功能进行脉冲控制(o41,o42)；
2：露点温度脉冲控制(o86,o87,o88)。此功能需要露点温度的信号，该信号需要主控器监测并通过数据通讯传输到控制器。
Help_da:
Kantvarmen kan styres på følgende måder:

0: Kantvarmen kører 100%

1: Kantvarmen pulseres ud fra dag og nat drift

2: Kantvarmen pulseres ud fra det aktuelle dug punkt. Dette kræver at dug punktet bliver sendt over netværket til møbelstyringen
Help_fr: 0: Toujours en marche 1: Pulsation en fonction du jour et de la nuit 2: Pulsation avec point de rosée. Cette fonction requiert un system manager
Help_es:
El antivaho puede controlarse de varias formas:
0: Antivaho funciona siempre.
1: Control por pulsos mediante la funcion dia/noche.
2: Control por pulsos usando la funcion de punto de rocio. Esta ultima funcion requiere una señal desde el System Manager.
Help_de:
The rail heat can be controlled in several ways: 


0: Railheat is running all the time 


1: Pulse control is used with a timer function following the day/night operation 


2: Pulse control is used with a dew point function. This function requires that a signal is received about the dew point value. The value is measured by a system manager and sent to the controller via the data communication.
Help_pt: O desembaçador pode ser controlador de várias formas. 0: Desemb. funcionando o tempo todo; 1: Controle de pulsos é utilizado com uma função timer, seguindo operação dia/noite; 2: Controle de pulsos é utilizado com função de cálculo do ponto de orvalho. Essa função requer que um sensor seja instalado no gerenciador do sistema, e que o sinal seja enviado ao controlador via rede.
Help_ru: Кантовый подогрев может управляться несколькими способами: 0: кантовый подогрев работает все время. 1: используется импульсное управление с функцией таймера следующего за дневным/ночным режимом. 2: используется импульсное управление с функцией точки росы. Функция требует получения сигнала о точке росы.
Help_it:
The rail heat can be controlled in several ways: 


0: Railheat is running all the time 


1: Pulse control is used with a timer function following the day/night operation 


2: Pulse control is used with a dew point function. This function requires that a signal is received about the dew point value. The value is measured by a system manager and sent to the controller via the data communication.

Name: Rail heat min ON cycle
Help:
Lowest permitted rail heat power. 
When the measured dew point is below the defined minimum limit the rail heat will run with the set minimum power
Help_en:
Lowest permitted rail heat power. 
When the measured dew point is below the defined minimum limit the rail heat will run with the set minimum power
Help_zh:
防结露最小开启占比
当露点温度比最小设定值低时，防结露按最小开启占比运行
Help_da: Mindst tilladte varmeeffekt når dugpunktet ligger under minimumsgrænsen
Help_fr:
Effet cordon chauffant admissible le plus faible. L’on règle ici le pourcentage de l’effet qui sera communiqué lorsque la valeur du point de
condensation est minimum.
Help_es: Minimo permitido para la activacion de antivaho. Cuando el punto de rocio medido esta por debajo del limite inferior entonces el antivaho funcionara a la minima potencia.
Help_de:
Lowest permitted rail heat power. 
When the measured dew point is below the defined minimum limit the rail heat will run with the set minimum power
Help_pt: Carga mínima permitida do desembaçador. Quando o valor de ponto de orvalho estiver abaixo do valor mínimo, o desembaçador irá atuar com carga mínima.
Help_ru: Наименьшая разрешенная мощность кантового подогрева. Когда измеренная точка росы ниже определенного минимального предела кантовый подогрев будет работать с установленной минимальной мощностью
Help_it:
Lowest permitted rail heat power. 
When the measured dew point is below the defined minimum limit the rail heat will run with the set minimum power

Name: Dewpoint min limit
Help: If the measuered dew point is below the set value the rail heat is running at minimum heat
Help_en: If the measuered dew point is below the set value the rail heat is running at minimum heat
Help_zh: 当露点温度比该设定值低时，防结露按最小占比运行
Help_da: Hvis det målte dugpunkt ligger under denne grænse, vil kantvarmen kører med minimum varmeeffekt
Help_fr: Valeur de point de rosée où le cordon chauffant est minimum. La fonction est développée précédemment dans le manuel.
Help_es: Si el punto de rocio medido esta por debajo de este ajuste, el antivaho funciona dando el minimo calor.
Help_de: If the measuered dew point is below the set value the rail heat is running at minimum heat
Help_pt: Se o ponto de orvalho medido estiver abaixo do setpoint, o desembaçador irá funcionar em carga mínima.
Help_ru: Если измеренная точка росы ниже установленного значения кантовый подогрев работает с минимальной мощностью
Help_it: If the measuered dew point is below the set value the rail heat is running at minimum heat

Name: Light control mode
Enum_zh: 1:白天和夜间,2:网络,3:门磁控制,4:网络（反馈）,5:数字量输入
Enum_es: 1:Dia y Noche,2:Via Bus (comunicaciones),3:Entrada Puerta,4:Red (en caso de fallo),5:Entr. Digital
Help:
Configuration of light function

1: Light is controlled via  day/night status 

2: Light is controlled via data communication and master control parameter "MC Light signal" 

3: Light is controlled by door contact on DI input. When the door is opened the relay will cut in. When the door is closed again there will be a time delay of two minutes before the light is switched off. 

4: As "2" but if there are any 15-minute network errors, the light will switch on and the night blind will open. 

5: Light is controlled via DI input signal
Help_en:
Configuration of light function

1: Light is controlled via  day/night status 

2: Light is controlled via data communication and master control parameter "MC Light signal" 

3: Light is controlled by door contact on DI input. When the door is opened the relay will cut in. When the door is closed again there will be a time delay of two minutes before the light is switched off. 

4: As "2" but if there are any 15-minute network errors, the light will switch on and the night blind will open. 

5: Light is controlled via DI input signal
Help_zh:
照明功能配置
1：照明依照白天/夜间信号控制；
2：照明通过数据通讯和主从控制参数"MC照明信号"控制；
3：照明通过DI门磁信号控制。当库门打开
时，照明打开；库门关闭时，2min延时后，照明关闭
4:同2，但是当通讯故障15min后照明和帘幕将被打开
Help_da:
Valg af lysfunktion:

1: Lys styres ud fra dag/nat status

2: Lys styres via netværkssignal

3: Lys styres ud fra dør kontakt på DI indgang. Når døren åbnes tændes lyset og når døren lukkes slukkes lyset efter 2 minutter

4: Lys styres ud fra netværkssignal, men hvis netværk bliver afbrudt i mere end 15 minutter tændes lyset automatisk

5: Lys styres via DI indgangssignal
Help_fr:
Configuration de la fonction d’éclairage1: L’éclairage s’active en fonction du jour et de la nuit 2: L’éclairage est commandé par la transmission de données et le signal MC 3: L’éclairage est commandé par le contact de porte défini dans sur l'entree DI., avec le réglage
2 ou 3. Le relais se ferme, lorsque la porte est ouverte. Après la fermeture de la porte, il y a un
laps de 2 minutes avant que la lumière soit éteinte.
Help_es:
Configuracion de la funcion de luces:
1: La luz se controla via el estado dia/noche
2: La luz se controla por el bus de comunicaciones con el parametro MC Ligh signal
3: La luz se controla con el contacto de puerta. Cuando se abre la puerta se enciende la luz y al cerrarse se mantiene 2 minutos encendida.
Help_de:
Configuration of light function

1: Light is controlled via  day/night status 

2: Light is controlled via data communication and master control parameter "MC Light signal" 

3: Light is controlled by door contact on DI input. When the door is opened the relay will cut in. When the door is closed again there will be a time delay of two minutes before the light is switched off. 

4: As "2" but if there are any 15-minute network errors, the light will switch on and the night blind will open. 

5: Light is controlled via DI input signal
Help_pt: Configuração da função de luzes. 1: Luzes são controladas via status dia/noite, 2: Luzes são controladas via rede e controle parâmetro MASTER, 3: Luzes são controladas por entrada digital de porta. Quando a porta estiver aberta o relé irá ativar. Quando a porta fechar haverá um atraso de dois minutos até as luzes serem apagadas.
Help_ru: Конфигурация функции света. 1: Свет управляется по статусу день/ночь. 2: Свет управляется через передачу данных и параметр контрольной функции "КФ Сигнал свет". 3: Свет управляется дверным контактом на входе DI. Когда дверь открыта реле включится.

Name: Light at Main switch OFF
Help:
Define how light and blinds are to be controlled at Main switch OFF 

0: Light is switched off and night blinds are open when the main switch is off 

1: Light and night blinds are independent of main switch.
Help_en:
Define how light and blinds are to be controlled at Main switch OFF 

0: Light is switched off and night blinds are open when the main switch is off 

1: Light and night blinds are independent of main switch.
Help_zh:
主开关关闭时照明和帘幕的控制方式
0：照明关闭，夜帘打开；
1：照明、夜帘控制与主开关无关
Help_da:
Vælg hvorledes lyset skal styres når reguleringen er stoppet via hovedafbryderen

0: Lys slukkes og natgardiener er åbne når reguleringen stoppes via hovedafbryderen

1: Lys og natgardin styres fortsat når reguleringen stoppes via hovedafbryderen
Help_fr: Définition de l’éclairage et du rideau de nuit 0: L'éclairage est arrêté et le rideau de nuit est ouvert lorsque l'interrupteur est sur arrêt. 1: L'éclairage et le rideau de nuit dépendent de l'interrupteur principal.
Help_es:
Definir como se controlan las luces y las cortinas al apagar el interruptor principal.
0: Luces apagadas y cortinas de noche abiertas al apagar el interruptor principal.
1: Luces y cortinas no se controlan con el interruptor principal.
Help_de:
Define how light and blinds are to be controlled at Main switch OFF 

0: Light is switched off and night blinds are open when the main switch is off 

1: Light and night blinds are independent of main switch.
Help_pt: Defina como as luzes e cortinas atuarão quando a chave principal = OFF. 0: luzes são desligadas e cortinas são abertas quando a chave principal estiver em OFF. 1: luzes e cortinas são independentes da chave principal.
Help_ru: Определяет как должны управляться чвет и шторки когда Главный выключатель ВЫКЛ. 0: Свет выключен и ночные шторки открыты когда главный выключатель выкл. 1: Свет и шторки не зависят от главного выключателя
Help_it:
Define how light and blinds are to be controlled at Main switch OFF 

0: Light is switched off and night blinds are open when the main switch is off 

1: Light and night blinds are independent of main switch.

Name_pt: Parada do vent no fechamento das cortinas

Help_da: Ved lukning af natgardin stoppes blæseren i den indstillede periode, for at sikre at gardinet kører korrekt ned

Help_it: When blinds are closing the fans are stopped in the defined time delay in order to ensure that the blinds are closed correctly

Name: Case cleaning mode
Help:
The status of the function can be followed here or the function can be started manually.

0 = Normal operation (no cleaning) 

1 = Only fans are running to defrost the evaporator. All other outputs are Off. 

2 = Cleaning with stopped fans. All outputs are Off. 

If the function is controlled by a digital input signal, the relevant status can be seen here in the menu.
Help_en:
The status of the function can be followed here or the function can be started manually.

0 = Normal operation (no cleaning) 

1 = Only fans are running to defrost the evaporator. All other outputs are Off. 

2 = Cleaning with stopped fans. All outputs are Off. 

If the function is controlled by a digital input signal, the relevant status can be seen here in the menu.
Help_zh:
此处，可设定该功能控制方式，或者手动启动该功能
0=正常运行（无清洗）
1=清洗时风扇运行，所有其他输出关闭
2=清洗时风扇停止，所有其他输出关闭
如果该功能通过DI输入信号控制，相关的状态可以在菜单看到。
Help_da:
Rengøringsprocedure kan gennemføres hér.

0: Rengøring er ikke startet

1: Rengøring er startet og blæser kører for at afrime fordamper

2: Al regulering er stoppet og rengøring kan foretages
Hvis rengøringen styres fra et digitalt indgangssignal, vil parameteren udlæse den aktuelle status af rengøringsproceduren
Help_fr:
Nettoyage du meuble
Permet de contrôler l’état de la fonction ou de la démarrer manuellement.
0=Fonctionnement normal (sans nettoyage)1=Nettoyage avec ventilateurs en marche. Toutes les autres sorties sont OFF.2=Nettoyage avec ventilateurs arrêtés. Toutes les sorties sont OFF.Si la fonction est commandée par un signal reçu à l’entrée DI1, DI2 ou DI3, l’état actuel figure dans ce menu.
Help_es:
El estado de la funcion se puede seguir aqui o la funcion se puede arrancar manualmente.
0: Operacion normal (no hay limpieza)
1: Ventiladores en funcionamiento para limpiar el evaporador (las demas salidas estan en OFF)
2: Limpieza con ventiladores parados, todas las demas salidas OFF.
Help_de:
The status of the function can be followed here or the function can be started manually.

0 = Normal operation (no cleaning) 

1 = Only fans are running to defrost the evaporator. All other outputs are Off. 

2 = Cleaning with stopped fans. All outputs are Off. 

If the function is controlled by a digital input signal, the relevant status can be seen here in the menu.
Help_pt: O status da função pode ser acompanhado aqui, ou a função pode ser iniciada automaticamente. 0: operação normal (sem limpeza); 1: Somente ventiladores funcionam para fazer degelo no evaporador; 2: Limpeza com ventiladores parados. Todas as saídas estão desligadas. Se a função for controlada por uma entrada digital, o status por ser visto no menu.
Help_ru: Статус функции можно отследить здесь или функция может быть запущена вручную. 0 = Нормальная работа (нет уборки). 1 = Работают только вентиляторы для оттайки испарителя. Все остальные выходы Выкл. 2 = Уборка с выключенными вентиляторами. Все выходы выкл.

Name: Display readout 1
Help: Read out of the temperature shown on the display
Help_en: Read out of the temperature shown on the display
Help_zh: 显示温度读数
Help_da: Udlæsning af displayets aktuelle temperatur visning
Help_fr: Valeur Afficheur
Help_es: Lectura de la temperatura que se esta mostrando en el display.
Help_de: Read out of the temperature shown on the display
Help_pt: Leitura display
Help_ru: Температура отображаемая на дисплее
Help_it: Read out of the temperature shown on the display

Name: Display air S4%
Help:
Signal to the display sensor. 
Here you have to define the ratio between the sensors which the display has to use. S3, S4 or a combination of the two. 

With setting 0% only S3 is used. 
With 100% only S4 is used
Help_en:
Signal to the display sensor. 
Here you have to define the ratio between the sensors which the display has to use. S3, S4 or a combination of the two. 

With setting 0% only S3 is used. 
With 100% only S4 is used
Help_zh:
定义显示温度的传感器信号。
此处设置显示温度的基准参考信号，S3、S4或S3和S4的加权。0%=S3，100%=S4
Help_da:
Valg af display føler. Hér definerer du hvilke følere der anvendes til display visningen S3, S4 eller en kombination af begge. 
Ved en indstilling på 0% anvendes udelukkende S3. Ved en indstilling på 100% anvendes udelukkende S4. Ved en indstilling imellem 1% og 99% anvendes en vægtning imellem de to følere.
Help_fr:
Sélectionner le signal pour l'affichage S4%
Ici, vous définissez le signal à afficher par l’affichage. S3, S4 ou une combinaison des 2.
Help_es: Definir el % de la sonda S4 que se muestra en el display. El resto será de la sonda S3. Ejemplo: si se quiere mostrar solo S3, poner este ajuste al 0%. Si se quiere mostrar solo S4, poner este ajuste al 100%.
Help_de:
Signal to the display sensor. 
Here you have to define the ratio between the sensors which the display has to use. S3, S4 or a combination of the two. 

With setting 0% only S3 is used. 
With 100% only S4 is used
Help_pt: Sinal para o display. Aqui você define o peso dos sensores que o display ira utilizar. S3, S4 ou uma combinação dos dois. Para 0% somente o S3 é utilizado. Com 100%, apenas S4.
Help_ru: Сигнал для дисплея. Здесь Вы определяете соотношение между датчиками, которое будет использовать дисплей. S3, S4 или их комбинация. При настройке 0% используется только S3. При 100% только S4.
Help_it:
Signal to the display sensor. 
Here you have to define the ratio between the sensors which the display has to use. S3, S4 or a combination of the two. 

With setting 0% only S3 is used. 
With 100% only S4 is used

Name: Display readout adjustment
Help:
Correction of the display´s temperature.
If the temperature at the products and the temperature received by the controller are not identical, an offset adjustment of the display temperature can be carried out."
Help_en:
Correction of the display´s temperature.
If the temperature at the products and the temperature received by the controller are not identical, an offset adjustment of the display temperature can be carried out."
Help_zh: 调整显示的温度读数。当货物温度或控制器接收的温度读数不准确时，可通过温度偏差调整，改变显示的读数。
Help_da: Korrektion af den løbende temperaturlæsning i displayet
Help_fr: Offset Afficheur
Help_es: Correccion de la lectura del display. Si la temperatura de los productos y la mostrada en el controlador no es igual, se puede ajustar el display, pero esto no afecta a la regulacion.
Help_de:
Correction of the display´s temperature.
If the temperature at the products and the temperature received by the controller are not identical, an offset adjustment of the display temperature can be carried out."
Help_pt: Correção da temperatura do display. Se a temperatura dos produtos e temperatura recebida pelo controlador não são idênticas, um ajuste pode ser feito.
Help_ru:
Коррекция температуры на дисплее. 
Если температура продукта и температура, полученная контроллером, не идентичны, можно выполнить корректировку смещения температуры на дисплее."
Help_it:
Correction of the display´s temperature.
If the temperature at the products and the temperature received by the controller are not identical, an offset adjustment of the display temperature can be carried out."

Help_es: Seleccione unidades entre ºC o ºF

Name: Display lock
Help: With this setting it is possible to lock the keypad operation of the local display. When not used for some time, the local display will lock the button operations and a special key combination is required in order to use the keypad
Help_en: With this setting it is possible to lock the keypad operation of the local display. When not used for some time, the local display will lock the button operations and a special key combination is required in order to use the keypad
Help_zh: 设置是否油现场显示器的按键锁定。显示器一段时间不操作后，按键将锁定，需要按特定按键组合才能恢复。
Help_da: Med denne indstilling er det muligt at blokere brugen af trykknapperne på displayet. Hvis display knapperne ikke har været anvendt et stykke tid vil knapperne blive deaktiveret. Herefter er en speciel tastekombination påkrævet for at anvende trykknapperne igen.
Help_fr: Ce paramètre permet de vérrouiller le clavier de l'afficheur local. Quand il n'est pas utilisé d'un certain temps, l'affhcieur local se vérouille et une combinaion de touche particulière est nécessaire pour utiliser à nouveau le clavier.
Help_es: Con este ajuste se puede bloquear el display si no se usa despues de un cierto tiempo, y es necesario una combinacion de teclas para poder usarlo de nuevo.
Help_de: With this setting it is possible to lock the keypad operation of the local display. When not used for some time, the local display will lock the button operations and a special key combination is required in order to use the keypad
Help_pt: Com essa configuração é possível travar a operação pelo display local. Quando inativo por muito tempo, o display local irá travar os botões e uma combinação específica de botões será necessária para utilizar o teclado.
Help_ru: Эта настройка позволяет блокировать клавиатуру локального дисплея. Если некоторое время не используются, кнопки локального дисплея блокируются, повторное использование возможно после нажатия специальной комбинации кнопок.
Help_it: With this setting it is possible to lock the keypad operation of the local display. When not used for some time, the local display will lock the button operations and a special key combination is required in order to use the keypad

Name: Alarm relay priority
Help:
Set which alarm priorities that are to activate the alarm relay: 

0=Not used, alarm relay is not used


1: High, alarm with high priority will activate relay


2: Medium, alarms with high or medium priority will activate the alarm relay


3: All, all alarms will activate alarm relay
Help_en:
Set which alarm priorities that are to activate the alarm relay: 

0=Not used, alarm relay is not used


1: High, alarm with high priority will activate relay


2: Medium, alarms with high or medium priority will activate the alarm relay


3: All, all alarms will activate alarm relay
Help_zh: 设置何种等级报警将激活报警继电器：0=不使用，不使用报警继电器；1=高，高等级报警将激活继电器；2=中，中或高等级将激活继电器；3=所有，所有报警将激活继电器
Help_da:
Vælg hvilke alarm prioriteter, der skal aktivere alarm relæet:
0: Alarm relæ anvendes ikke
1: Kun højprioritetsalarmer aktiverer alarm relæet
2: Høj- og mediumprioritetsalarmer aktiverer relæet
3: Alle alarmer aktiverer alarm relæet
Help_fr: Regalge des priorité pour l'acivation du relais d'alarme: 0= Non utilisé, le relais d'alarme n'est pas utilisé 1: Haut, Les alarme de niveau haut active le relais d'alarme 2: Moyen, Les alarmes de niveau Haut et Moyen enclenche le relais d'alarme 3: Tous, toutes les alarmes activent le relais d'alarme
Help_es:
Seleccione con que prioridad se debe activar el rele de alarma:
0= No se usa el rele de alarma
1= El rele de alarma se activa con alarmas de prioridad alta.
2 = El rele de alarmas se activa con alarmas de prioridad media y alta.
3 = El rele de alarma se activa con todas las alarmas.
Help_de:
Set which alarm priorities that are to activate the alarm relay: 

0=Not used, alarm relay is not used


1: High, alarm with high priority will activate relay


2: Medium, alarms with high or medium priority will activate the alarm relay


3: All, all alarms will activate alarm relay
Help_pt: Defina quais prioridades de alarme ativam o relé de alarme. 0= não utilizado, 1=Alto, este alarme ativa o rele, 2=Médio, alarmes com alta e média prioridade ativam o relé, 3=Todos, todos os alarmes ativam o relé
Help_ru: Установите аварийные приоритеты при которых активируется аварийное реле: 0=не используется, аварийное реле не используется, 1: Высокий, при аварии с высокм приоритетом реле будет активировано 2: Средний, при авариях с высоким и средним приоритетом аварийное реле будет активировано 3: Все, все аварии приведут к активации аварийного реле
Help_it:
Set which alarm priorities that are to activate the alarm relay: 

0=Not used, alarm relay is not used


1: High, alarm with high priority will activate relay


2: Medium, alarms with high or medium priority will activate the alarm relay


3: All, all alarms will activate alarm relay

Name: Mute alarm
Help: When muting alarms, the alarm relay will stop signalling the alarm until a new alarm arises
Help_en: When muting alarms, the alarm relay will stop signalling the alarm until a new alarm arises
Help_zh: 当报警禁用时，报警继电器将停止，直到新的报警产生。
Help_da: Når man stopper alarmgiveren vil alarmrelæet stoppe med at signallere alarm indtil en ny alarm opstår.
Help_fr: En mettant en sourdine les alarmes, le relais d'alarmes ne signal plus rien tant qu'une nouvelle alarmes n'est pas arrivées
Help_es: Cuando se siliencian las alarmas, el rele de alarma deja de estar activo hasta que aparece una nueva alarma.
Help_de: When muting alarms, the alarm relay will stop signalling the alarm until a new alarm arises
Help_pt: Ao silenciar os alarmes, o relé de alarme irá parar de sinalizar os alarmes, até que um novo alarme ative.
Help_ru: При выключении аварийной сигнализации аварийное реле перестанет сигнализировать об аварии до момента появления новой аварии
Help_it: When muting alarms, the alarm relay will stop signalling the alarm until a new alarm arises

Name: High temperature - Priority
Help:
Select the priority of the alarms associated to the alarm group. 
Be aware - by selecting "Disable" the alarms will not be shown on the display or be routed to the alarm relay or to the network.
Help_en:
Select the priority of the alarms associated to the alarm group. 
Be aware - by selecting "Disable" the alarms will not be shown on the display or be routed to the alarm relay or to the network.
Help_zh: 选择报警组中报警的等级。注意-选择“禁用”后报警将不会在控制器及主控器中显示或在继电器中输出。
Help_da:
Vælg prioriteten for de alarmer, der hører til den pågælende alarmgruppe.
Pas på - hvis man vælger "Ej brugt" vil de pågældende alarmer ikke blive vist i displayet og de vil ikke blive sendt til alarmrelæet eller ud på netværket.
Help_fr: Sélectionnez la priorité du groupe d'alarme. ATTENTION, en sélectionnant "Désactivé", l'alarme ne sera plus visible via l'afficheur et ne sera pas envoyé sur les relais d'alarme ou le réseau.
Help_es: Seleccione la prioridad de las alarmas asociadas al grupo de alarmas. Si se selecciona -Deshabilitado- las alarmas no se mostaran en el display ni se enviaran a ningun sitio.
Help_de:
Select the priority of the alarms associated to the alarm group. 
Be aware - by selecting "Disable" the alarms will not be shown on the display or be routed to the alarm relay or to the network.
Help_pt: Selecione a prioridade dos alarmes associados ao grupo de alarmes. Cuidado - ao selecionar "Desabilitar" os alarmes não serão mostrados no display ou guiados ao relé de alarme nem rede.
Help_ru: Выберите приоритет связанный с группой аварий. Внимание, выбрав "отключено" аварии не будут отображаться на дисплее или активировать реле и отправляться по сети
Help_it:

Help_ru: Эта команда сохранит текущие параметры как заводские (заводские параметры будут перезаписаны)

GroupName_da: Main menu|Avancerede funktioner|Ekspert indstillinger for indsprøjtning
GroupName_pt: Main menu|Nível de especialista|Advanced injection control
Name: Superheat ctrl. mode A
Help:
Select how to control the superheat of the evaporator. At adaptive control the superheat reference is adapted automatically to give the best utilization of the evaporator surface. 
At load based control the superheat reference is increased at high loads
Help_en:
Select how to control the superheat of the evaporator. At adaptive control the superheat reference is adapted automatically to give the best utilization of the evaporator surface. 
At load based control the superheat reference is increased at high loads
Help_zh:
选择如何控制过热度
在调节模式，将自动选取符合蒸发器表面状态的过热度参考值。在基于负荷模式下，在高负荷下过热度将增加。
Help_da:
Vælg hvordan overhedningen på fordamperen skal reguleres. 
Ved adaptiv styring tilpasses overhedningsreferencen automatisk så overfladen på fordamperen udnyttes bedst muligt. 
Ved belastningsstyret overhedning øges referencen ved højere belastning
Help_fr: Mode Ctrl. Surchauffe
Help_es: Seleccione como debe controlarse el recalentamiento en el evaporador. En el control ADAPTATIVO la referencia se adapta automaticamene para obtener la mayor superficie de intercambio en el evaporador. En el control en base a la CARGA, el recalentamiento aumenta si la carga es mayor.
Help_de:
Select how to control the superheat of the evaporator. At adaptive control the superheat reference is adapted automatically to give the best utilization of the evaporator surface. 
At load based control the superheat reference is increased at high loads
Help_pt: Selecione a modalidade de controle do superaquecimento através do evaporador. Em controle adaptativo, a referência de superaquecimento é adaptada automaticamente de modo a garantir o melhor rendimento.
Help_ru: Выберите как управлять пергревом испарителя. При адаптивном управлении перегревом уставка автоатически адаптируется для обеспечения наилучшего использования поверхности испарителя. При управлении в зависимости от нагрузки  уставка перегрева увеличивается при высоких нагрузках
Help_it:
Select how to control the superheat of the evaporator. At adaptive control the superheat reference is adapted automatically to give the best utilization of the evaporator surface. 
At load based control the superheat reference is increased at high loads

Name: High temperature alarm A
Help: The alarm temperature has been above the max alarm limit for a longer time period than the set alarm delay.
Help_en: The alarm temperature has been above the max alarm limit for a longer time period than the set alarm delay.
Help_zh: 当报警温度超出该值，经过报警延时时间后，将产生高温报警。
Help_da: Alarm temperaturen har ligget over den indstillede øvre alarm grænse i længere tid end den indstillede alarm forsinkelse.
Help_fr: Alarme Temp Haute
Help_es: La temperatura ha llegado al limite programado y se ha superado el tiempo de retraso programado.
Help_de: The alarm temperature has been above the max alarm limit for a longer time period than the set alarm delay.
Help_pt: A temperatura de alarme esteve acima do limite de alarme por um tempo maior que o definido no atraso.
Help_ru: Температура была выше максимального аварийного предела в течение более длительного времени чем установленная задержка аварии
Help_it: The alarm temperature has been above the max alarm limit for a longer time period than the set alarm delay.

Name: Low temperature alarm A
Help: The alarm temperature has been below the min alarm limit for a longer time period than the set alarm delay.
Help_en: The alarm temperature has been below the min alarm limit for a longer time period than the set alarm delay.
Help_zh: 当报警温度低于该值，经过报警延时时间后，将产生低温报警。
Help_da: Alarm temperaturen har ligget under den indstillede nedre alarm grænse i længere tid end den indstillede alarm forsinkelse.
Help_fr: Alarme Temp Basse
Help_es: La temperatura ha llegado al limite bajo programado y se ha superado el tiempo de retraso programado.
Help_de: The alarm temperature has been below the min alarm limit for a longer time period than the set alarm delay.
Help_pt: A temperatura de alarme esteve abaixo do limite de alarme por um tempo maior que o definido no atraso.
Help_ru: Температура была ниже минимального аварийного предела в течение более длительного времени чем установленная задержка аварии
Help_it: The alarm temperature has been below the min alarm limit for a longer time period than the set alarm delay.

Name: Door open alarm
Help: The door has been open for a too long time
Help_en: The door has been open for a too long time
Help_zh: 门打开时间过长报警
Help_da: Døren har været åben i for lang tid
Help_fr: La porte est ouverte depuis trop longtemps.
Help_es: La puerta lleva abierta demasiado tiempo.
Help_de: The door has been open for a too long time
Help_pt: Alarme de porta aberta
Help_ru: Дверь открыта в течение очнь долго
Help_it: The door has been open for a too long time

Name: Max defrost hold time exceeded
Help: The controller has been waiting longer time than permitted after a co-ordinated defrost.
Help_en: The controller has been waiting longer time than permitted after a co-ordinated defrost.
Help_zh: 协同除霜模式下控制器等待时间超出设定值
Help_da: Regulatoren har ventet længere end den maksimalt tilladdelige tid efter en koordineret afrimning
Help_fr: Attente maximum après dégivrage coordonné
Help_es: Se ha superado el limite de tiempo que el controlador espera a otros controladores en un desescarche coordinado.
Help_de: The controller has been waiting longer time than permitted after a co-ordinated defrost.
Help_pt: O controlador aguardou muito tempo por um degelo coordenado
Help_ru: Контроллер ждал дольше времени, чем разрешено после координированной оттайки
Help_it: The controller has been waiting longer time than permitted after a co-ordinated defrost.

Name: Refrigerant not selected
Help: The refrigerant has not been selected hence control can not be initiated
Help_en: The refrigerant has not been selected hence control can not be initiated
Help_zh: 未选择制冷剂，控制无法进行
Help_da: Kølemiddel er ikke blevet indstillet i regulatoren. Reguleringen kan ikke startes før end dette er sket.
Help_fr: Le réfrigérant n'a pas été sélectionné dans la liste, le régulateur ne peut démarrer
Help_es: No se ha seleccionado refrigerante en el controlador.
Help_de: The refrigerant has not been selected hence control can not be initiated
Help_pt: O refrigerante não foi selecionado, portanto o controle não pode ser iniciado.
Help_ru: Хладагент не выбран, управление не может быть запущено.
Help_it: The refrigerant has not been selected hence control can not be initiated

Name: Main switch set OFF
Help: The controller manin switch has been set to either Stop or Manaual control. Alternatively a digital input set up for "main switch" function, has stopped control
Help_en: The controller manin switch has been set to either Stop or Manaual control. Alternatively a digital input set up for "main switch" function, has stopped control
Help_zh: 主开关被改到关闭或者手动控制，或者通过外部DI信号的“主开关”功能关闭主开关，当前控制已停止。
Help_da: Reguleringen er blevet stoppet ved at hovedafbryderen er sat i  position "Stop" eller "Manuel overstyring". Alternativt er reguleringen stoppet via et digital indgangssignal der er sat op til funktionen "Hovedafbryder"
Help_fr: L'interrupteur principale du régulateur a été mis soit sur arret soit sur manuel. Ce peut etre soit via l'entrée DI, soit via le parmètre.
Help_es: El controlador se ha parado por el interruptor principal interno o externo (DI).
Help_de: The controller manin switch has been set to either Stop or Manaual control. Alternatively a digital input set up for "main switch" function, has stopped control
Help_pt: A chave principal do controlador foi definida para parar ou para controle manual. Alternativamente uma entrada digital definida para chave principal também pode ter parado o sistema.
Help_ru: Главный выключатель контроллера был установлен в положение отключения или ручного управления. Или цифровой вход с функцией "главного выключателя" остановил управление
Help_it: The controller manin switch has been set to either Stop or Manaual control. Alternatively a digital input set up for "main switch" function, has stopped control

Name: Case in cleaning mode
Help: A case cleaning operation has been started on a case
Help_en: A case cleaning operation has been started on a case
Help_zh: 设备清洗已经激活
Help_da: En rengøringsprocedure er blevet startet
Help_fr: Meuble en nettoyage
Help_es: Se ha iniciado el modo Limpieza en el evaporador.
Help_de: A case cleaning operation has been started on a case
Help_pt: Foi iniciado o modo de limpeza
Help_ru: Уборка витрины запущена
Help_it: A case cleaning operation has been started on a case

Name_zh: 超出最大除霜时间 A
Name_pt: Tempo máximo de degelo excedido A

Help_en: The last defrost cycle has stopped on time instead of set temperature
Help_zh: 上一次除霜超出最大除霜时间停止，而不是达到设定温度停止
Help_da: Den sidste afrimning er blevet stoppet på tid fremfor på den valgte temperatur
Help_fr: Le dernier cycle de dégivrage a été areté en temps au lieu du seuil de température.
Help_es: El ultimo ciclo de desescarche ha terminado por tiempo y esta programado para hacerlo por temperatura.
Help_de: The last defrost cycle has stopped on time instead of set temperature
Help_pt: O último ciclo de degelo parou por tempo em vez de temperatura
Help_ru: Последний цикл оттайки был остановлен по времени, а не по температуре

Name: Main switch
Help:
Start / stop of refrigeration. 
With this setting refrigeration can be started, stopped or a manual override of the outputs can be allowed. (For manual control the value is set at -1. Then the outputs can be force controlled. Start / stop of refrigeration can also be accomplished with the external switch function connected to a DI input.
Stopped control will give a ”Main switch OFF" alarm.
Help_en:
Start / stop of refrigeration. 
With this setting refrigeration can be started, stopped or a manual override of the outputs can be allowed. (For manual control the value is set at -1. Then the outputs can be force controlled. Start / stop of refrigeration can also be accomplished with the external switch function connected to a DI input.
Stopped control will give a ”Main switch OFF" alarm.
Help_zh:
制冷起/停。可以通过该参数开启，停止和手动控制输出。（需要手动控制时，r12=-
1。可以强制控制输出。制冷起/停控制也可通过外部开关量信号实现(DI)。
制冷停止时，控制器将显示“Standby alarm（待机模式）”
Help_da: Start / stop af regulering. Med denne indstilling kan reguleringen startes, stoppes eller sættes i manuel overstyring. Ved manuel overstyring kan udgangene overstyres. Reguleringen kan også startes og stoppes vie et digitalt indgangssignal, hvis en sådan indgang er sat op.Når reguleringen stoppes aktiveres en alarm, for at gøre opmærksom på dette.
Help_fr:
Marche / Arrêt du régulateur
Avec ce paramètre, le régulateur peut être démarré, arrêté ou une commande manuelle des sorties peut être autorisée. (Pour le contrôle manuel, la valeur est définie sur -1).
Help_es: Paro/Marcha de la refrigeración. Con este ajuste la refrigeracion se inicia, se para o se pone el controlador en manual (ajustado en este caso un -1). Si se pone en manual, se puede actuar sobre las salidas. Tambien puede haber un interruptor externo en una entrada digital.
Help_de:
Start / stop of refrigeration. 
With this setting refrigeration can be started, stopped or a manual override of the outputs can be allowed. (For manual control the value is set at -1. Then the outputs can be force controlled. Start / stop of refrigeration can also be accomplished with the external switch function connected to a DI input.
Stopped control will give a ”Main switch OFF" alarm.
Help_pt: Função início/parada. Com essa configuração a refrigeração pode ser iniciada, parada ou ter as saídas colocadas para manual. Para controle manual o valor deve ser definido para -1, e então as saídas podem ser forçadas. Inicio/parada da refrigeração pode ser feita com a chave externa conectada à uma DI.
Help_ru:
Включение/выключение охлаждения. Этот параметр запускает регулирование, останавливает или переводит в режим ручного управления выходами. (Для режима ручного управлениянужно выбрать значение -1. 
Тогда выходами можно управлять принудительно. Запуск/остановека охлаждения также может быть осуществлена через внешний цифровой вход.
Help_it:
Start / stop of refrigeration. 
With this setting refrigeration can be started, stopped or a manual override of the outputs can be allowed. (For manual control the value is set at -1. Then the outputs can be force controlled. Start / stop of refrigeration can also be accomplished with the external switch function connected to a DI input.
Stopped control will give a ”Main switch OFF" alarm.

Help:
Selection of application 
The controller covers several applications for control of a refrigerated case. Here you set which of the possible applications is required.
This menu can only be set when regulation is stopped, i.e. “r12 Main Switch” is set to 0.
Help_en:
Selection of application 
The controller covers several applications for control of a refrigerated case. Here you set which of the possible applications is required.
This menu can only be set when regulation is stopped, i.e. “r12 Main Switch” is set to 0.
Help_zh: 选择应用类型。控制器包含多种制冷应用类型，可在此处选择需要的一种。该参数只有在控制停止时才能更改，如r12=0的时候。
Help_da: Valg af anvendelse. Regulatoren dækker flere anvendelsesmuligheder for styring af et kølemøbel. Hér vælger du den anvendelse, der passer til det pågældende møbel eller kølerum. Værdien kan kun ændres når hovedafbryderen er sat i OFF position.
Help_fr: Selection de l'application disponible dans le régulateur. Ce paramètre n'est réglable que lorsque le régulateur est a l'arret, ex: "r12 inter Principal" réglé à 0.
Help_es: Seleccion de la aplicación. El controlador tiene una serie de aplicaciones de refrigeracion dependiendo de este ajuste. Este parametro solo se puede cambiar si el interruptor principal esta parado.
Help_de:
Selection of application 
The controller covers several applications for control of a refrigerated case. Here you set which of the possible applications is required.
This menu can only be set when regulation is stopped, i.e. “r12 Main Switch” is set to 0.
Help_pt: Seleção da aplicação. O controlador cobre diversas aplicações para controle refrigerado. Aqui você define qual delas será usada. Este menu só pode ser alterado com funcionamento PARADO, ou seja, r12=0.
Help_ru: Выбор применения. Контроллер охватывает несколько вариантов управления охлаждаемой витриной. Здесь Вы выбираете какое  требуется применение из возможных. В этом меню можно меять настройки только когда регулирование остановлено, например "r12 Главный Выключатель" настроен на 0.
Help_it:
Selection of application 
The controller covers several applications for control of a refrigerated case. Here you set which of the possible applications is required.
This menu can only be set when regulation is stopped, i.e. “r12 Main Switch” is set to 0.

Name: Main switch
Help:
Start / stop of refrigeration. 
With this setting refrigeration can be started, stopped or a manual override of the outputs can be allowed. (For manual control the value is set at -1. Then the outputs can be force controlled. Start / stop of refrigeration can also be accomplished with the external switch function connected to a DI input.
Stopped control will give a ”Main switch OFF" alarm.
Help_en:
Start / stop of refrigeration. 
With this setting refrigeration can be started, stopped or a manual override of the outputs can be allowed. (For manual control the value is set at -1. Then the outputs can be force controlled. Start / stop of refrigeration can also be accomplished with the external switch function connected to a DI input.
Stopped control will give a ”Main switch OFF" alarm.
Help_zh:
制冷起/停。可以通过该参数开启，停止和手动控制输出。（需要手动控制时，r12=-
1。可以强制控制输出。制冷起/停控制也可通过外部开关量信号实现(DI)。
制冷停止时，控制器将显示“Standby alarm（待机模式）”
Help_da: Start / stop af regulering. Med denne indstilling kan reguleringen startes, stoppes eller sættes i manuel overstyring. Ved manuel overstyring kan udgangene overstyres. Reguleringen kan også startes og stoppes vie et digitalt indgangssignal, hvis en sådan indgang er sat op.Når reguleringen stoppes aktiveres en alarm, for at gøre opmærksom på dette.
Help_fr:
Marche / Arrêt du régulateur
Avec ce paramètre, le régulateur peut être démarré, arrêté ou une commande manuelle des sorties peut être autorisée. (Pour le contrôle manuel, la valeur est définie sur -1).
Help_es: Paro/Marcha de la refrigeración. Con este ajuste la refrigeracion se inicia, se para o se pone el controlador en manual (ajustado en este caso un -1). Si se pone en manual, se puede actuar sobre las salidas. Tambien puede haber un interruptor externo en una entrada digital.
Help_de:
Start / stop of refrigeration. 
With this setting refrigeration can be started, stopped or a manual override of the outputs can be allowed. (For manual control the value is set at -1. Then the outputs can be force controlled. Start / stop of refrigeration can also be accomplished with the external switch function connected to a DI input.
Stopped control will give a ”Main switch OFF" alarm.
Help_pt: Função início/parada. Com essa configuração a refrigeração pode ser iniciada, parada ou ter as saídas colocadas para manual. Para controle manual o valor deve ser definido para -1, e então as saídas podem ser forçadas. Inicio/parada da refrigeração pode ser feita com a chave externa conectada à uma DI.
Help_ru:
Включение/выключение охлаждения. Этот параметр запускает регулирование, останавливает или переводит в режим ручного управления выходами. (Для режима ручного управлениянужно выбрать значение -1. 
Тогда выходами можно управлять принудительно. Запуск/остановека охлаждения также может быть осуществлена через внешний цифровой вход.
Help_it:
Start / stop of refrigeration. 
With this setting refrigeration can be started, stopped or a manual override of the outputs can be allowed. (For manual control the value is set at -1. Then the outputs can be force controlled. Start / stop of refrigeration can also be accomplished with the external switch function connected to a DI input.
Stopped control will give a ”Main switch OFF" alarm.

Help:
Selection of application 
The controller covers several applications for control of a refrigerated case. Here you set which of the possible applications is required.
This menu can only be set when regulation is stopped, i.e. “r12 Main Switch” is set to 0.
Help_en:
Selection of application 
The controller covers several applications for control of a refrigerated case. Here you set which of the possible applications is required.
This menu can only be set when regulation is stopped, i.e. “r12 Main Switch” is set to 0.
Help_zh: 选择应用类型。控制器包含多种制冷应用类型，可在此处选择需要的一种。该参数只有在控制停止时才能更改，如r12=0的时候。
Help_da: Valg af anvendelse. Regulatoren dækker flere anvendelsesmuligheder for styring af et kølemøbel. Hér vælger du den anvendelse, der passer til det pågældende møbel eller kølerum. Værdien kan kun ændres når hovedafbryderen er sat i OFF position.
Help_fr: Selection de l'application disponible dans le régulateur. Ce paramètre n'est réglable que lorsque le régulateur est a l'arret, ex: "r12 inter Principal" réglé à 0.
Help_es: Seleccion de la aplicación. El controlador tiene una serie de aplicaciones de refrigeracion dependiendo de este ajuste. Este parametro solo se puede cambiar si el interruptor principal esta parado.
Help_de:
Selection of application 
The controller covers several applications for control of a refrigerated case. Here you set which of the possible applications is required.
This menu can only be set when regulation is stopped, i.e. “r12 Main Switch” is set to 0.
Help_pt: Seleção da aplicação. O controlador cobre diversas aplicações para controle refrigerado. Aqui você define qual delas será usada. Este menu só pode ser alterado com funcionamento PARADO, ou seja, r12=0.
Help_ru: Выбор применения. Контроллер охватывает несколько вариантов управления охлаждаемой витриной. Здесь Вы выбираете какое  требуется применение из возможных. В этом меню можно меять настройки только когда регулирование остановлено, например "r12 Главный Выключатель" настроен на 0.
Help_it:
Selection of application 
The controller covers several applications for control of a refrigerated case. Here you set which of the possible applications is required.
This menu can only be set when regulation is stopped, i.e. “r12 Main Switch” is set to 0.
